(7, NULL, 'Western Caribbean Cruise', 'Swingers Cruise | Couples Cruise | November Couples Cruise', '<h2><strong>Independence of the Seas</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Labadee, Roatan &amp; Cozumel</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px">2014 will be the first Adults only Charter from FORT LALUDERDALE, and it will be on the newest of the FREEDOM FAMILY; the &ldquo;INDEPENDENCE OF THE SEAS.&rdquo; This is another clothing optional experience on the pool decks and in our massive Play Room.<br />\r\nJoin over 1,800 couples for another <em><strong>COUPLES CRUISE</strong></em> adventure where you Set the rules for you and your partner and time to full fill the fantasies that both of you have always dreamed about. Incredible eye candy by the pool or be surrounded by hundreds of couples that dress to impress in the evening.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you like Mardi Gras, Fantasy Fest and <em><strong>Clothing Optional Beaches</strong></em> and Great destinations, then its time party on a COUPLES CRUISE and celebrate your Independence.<br />\r\nJoin us for the largest lifestyle party at sea with over 1,800 couples<br />\r\nThe itinerary of Labadee, Jamaica and Cozumel is one of the best groups of ports with some of the best custom excursions you will ever find. From spectacular clothing optional diving, snorkeling and beach parties, to a private island where we will have the entire island (Labadee) to ourselves, there are many exotic and erotic adventures for you.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nOf course, our favorite time is on board the ship. The Independence of the Seas has so many different venues and places to party; you will have lots of choices when it comes to music and activities. Every night is a theme night, so count on being sexy and meeting other sexy couples from all around the world on this historic Party at Sea.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nYou will have the INDEPENDENCE to take a skinny dip in any of the four swimming pools, or six hot tub whirlpools, that are on board. The INDEPENDENCE is over 150,000 tons and 1120 ft. long, making it one of the 3 largest cruise ships in the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn Deck 5, you can stroll down the promenade and see our red light district. You can visit multiple shops - do a slice of pizza or get something sweet the CUPCAKE CUPBOARD.<br />\r\nRelax with that perfect vintage at the Wine Bar and do some people watching. Go down a few decks below to STUDIO B and do a spin on the ice-staking rink or be part of the crowd with ice-skating spectacular shows. Ever tried the rock climbing wall or the FLOW RIDER. It&rsquo;s all your choice and your Independence.<br />\r\nThere is just so much to do a COUPLES CRUISE and much more than what is on board. We visit some of the best ports in the Caribbean from our own private island of LABADEE, to HONDURAS and the beautiful port of ROATAN, and then soak up the sun with our private excursion in COZUMEL.<br />\r\nEvery night is the perfect chance to explore your INDEPENDENCE; with multiple music venues you will find the right place for you and your partner. Each night offers you a<br />\r\nDifferent exotic themes - go ahead and experience your INDEPENDENCE.</span></h2>\r\n', 'img_96180.jpg', '2014-11-15 00:00:00', '2014-11-22 00:00:00', 'western-caribbean-cruise', 'Join over 1,800 couples for another COUPLES CRUISE adventure where you Set the rules for you and your partner and time to full fill the fantasies that both of you have always dreamed about.', 'Swingers Cruise, Couples Cruise, November Couples Cruise', 1, '2014-10-01 12:44:43', 3, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(14, NULL, 'Hawaiian Paradise Cruise 2015 ', 'Non-Stop Hawaiian Paradise Cruise Adventure for Singles', 'Enjoy a 7 day Hawaiian adventure cruise with other singles aboard the beautiful Pride of America Cruise ship. Make new friends and enjoy activities like island hiking (sunrise at 10,000 feet anyone?), hula dancing, luaus, ATV trips, helicopter flights, even a night sail past Mt. Kilauea.&nbsp; There is of course everything else you would expect like, surfing, suntans, lush mountains, playful whales off the Napali Coast.&nbsp; Best of all you can enjoy the sunrise and late night parties on a different island every day.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAboard the Pride of America, we&rsquo;ll be visiting the 5 top places in Hawaii (Honolulu, Maui, Hilo, Kona and Kauai). &nbsp;&nbsp;Come for Hawaii and explore all of your fantasies with our action packed itinerary.', 'pride-of-am0.jpg', '2015-05-24 00:00:00', '2015-05-30 00:00:00', 'hawaiian-paradise-cruise-2015', 'Enjoy a 7 day Hawaiian adventure cruise with other singles aboard the beautiful Pride of America Cruise ship. Make new friends and enjoy activities like island hiking (sunrise at 10,000 feet anyone?), hula dancing, luaus, ATV trips, helicopter flights, even a night sail past Mt. Kilauea.  ', 'Singles Cruise Hawaiian Paradise Party Vacation', 1, '2014-10-01 13:53:16', 3, 237, NULL, NULL),
(15, NULL, '7 Night Caribbean Getaway SINGLES Cruise', '7 Night Caribbean Getaway SINGLES Cruise!', 'Sail through the islands of the Eastern Caribbean as you spend 7 nights aboard the amazing new Norwegian Getaway! Depart from sunny Miami and make your way to the beautiful beaches of St. Maarten; snorkel the coral reefs of St. Thomas as you take in the views of one of the most spectacular harbors in the world; or have incredible adventures in Nassau at one of the many casinos or nightclubs!<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhen you join Singles Cruise on this amazing vacation, you&#39;ll experience all the fabulous amenities of the Norwegian Getaway PLUS a special invitation to all the exclusive singles activities we&#39;ll be throwing onboard! Every cruise is a little different but here are a few examples that may be on your next cruise: Complimentary Cocktail Parties, Complimentary Dining, Costume/Theme Nights, Private Dance Lessons, Speed Dating, Pub Crawls, and Karaoke Parties. Singles Shore excursions are practically limitless and include snorkeling, swimming with dolphins, sailing, ziplining, beach parties, cave tubing, hiking and MUCH more! Cruise ships cater to casino lovers and show stoppers! Live bands, comedy clubs, Las Vegas style production shows and deck parties are all included in your fabulous cruise vacation.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe benefit of booking a singles cruise with us is that you will get to enjoy an exciting cruise vacation and at the same time, meet and travel with a large number of single adults. We all know how hard it is to match up your vacation time with your friends and family, so we offer an easy way for you to travel on your own, but not be on your own (We can even match you up with a roommate!). On a &ldquo;regular&rdquo; cruise, you may meet a few singles here and there on the ship, but you won&rsquo;t be guaranteed a fun group of adults that you can hang out with. Our guests always tell us how nice it is to see friendly faces from our group out and about on the ship, and to have some new friends to hit the beach or take a snorkeling tour together. Our friendly and professional hosts coordinate fun events throughout your trip and you are provided an itinerary of the scheduled events. You can join in whenever you like - it&rsquo;s your vacation!<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nOur fantastic room rates and room options give you control over your cruising experience as well as your budget. With food, non-alcoholic drinks, entertainment, and all fees and taxes covered, we take care of all of the little things so you can focus on the big things and create the perfect cruise experience. Even better, join us before the cruise at our select pre-cruise hotel and &quot;Get Together&quot; in Miami. It&#39;s a great opportunity to meet and socialize with your fellow travelling companions before you board the ship!<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nJoin tons of other singles as you experience all that this trip has to offer and get a quote today! The memories and all your new found friendships will last a lifetime!', 'norwegian-getaway0.jpg', '2015-02-21 00:00:00', '2015-02-28 00:00:00', '7-night-caribbean-getaway-singles-cruise', '', '', 1, '2014-10-01 14:47:02', 3, 236, NULL, NULL),
