(115, 36, 1, 'Greece Party Tour 2015', 'Greek Island Party - Mykonos Party - Ios Island Party - Satorini', 0, 1, 0, 'Vacationparties.com will be in Greece again for our second annual Greek Islands Party Tour. Once again visiting the popular Islands of Mykonos, Paros, Ios and Santorini. This time we have extended the trip to 12 days, giving you enough time to get over the jet lag and enjoy and enjoy the best of what each island has to offer.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Greek islands are known world wide for hosting the most amazing parties during the Summer Months. Vacation party-seekers from all over the globe gather on these islands for 3 to 7 days at a time, and the atmosphere is absolutely electric. From the tiny night-clubs in the towns to the dozens of beach parties happening both day and night time, the Greek Islands is second to none when it comes to having the ultimate party vacation.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWe will be your personal tour guide on this trip, taking your from island to island and ensuring that you enjoy the best of each island in the 2-3 days that you will spend on each. From restaurant reservations, reserving beach chairs to getting you into the VIP booth of different night clubs that we visit, we are there to take the headache away so you can focus on having fun.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe trip will start off with visiting the high-energy pary islands such as Mykonos and Ios, then we will close of the tour with the more relaxing a picturesque islands like Santorini. The twelve days will provide you with the perfect blend of wild parties, mixed with romantic relaxation and site seeing, not to mention the amazing food that is available in Greece.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe invite you to come party with us in Greece in 2015!<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 'greece0.jpg', '', '1402077850_', '1402077850_', '2015-06-17', '2015-06-30', 9, '', '', 0, NULL, 1, 'greece-party-tour-2015', 'Join Vacationparties.com in Greece for a 12 day guided party tour of the islands of Mykonos, Paros, Ios and Santorini.', 'Mykonos, Paros, Ios, Santorini, Greek Islands Party, ', 1, 2, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
