INSERT INTO `faqs` (`id`, `question`, `answer`, `status`, `added_on`) VALUES
(19, 'WhatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s included?', 'Every booking is unique and customizable. All-inclusive resorts generally include food, drinks, alcohol, and tips/fees/taxes right in their daily rate. Other resorts may offer fewer amenities, but with a more competitive rate. Your Personal Travel Specialist will clearly explain the details of any package you may be interested in, so if you have any questions about what is and isnÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t included, feel free to ***contact us for assistance***.', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(4, 'Do I have to be Naked? ', 'Many of the Resorts we take over are Ã¢â‚¬Å“clothing optionalÃ¢â‚¬Â which means it a choice. If you are comfortable and want to go naked, feel free, however you can also be Topless or not naked at all. And for these resorts there is no nudity in the Dining areas. The only time Nudity is required is on a Nudist Resort, which of course you would be aware of at time of booking.', 1, '2013-08-12'),
(14, 'Why book with VacationParties.com?', 'The VacationParties.com experience is known throughout the travel community to be unique, hassle-free, and filled with endless possibilities. Our Signature Events are truly the best time you can have on vacation, and even independent travelers have come to rely on us for our knowledge and integrity in dealing with our clients and their needs. The value-added services we provide (VIP check-in, first-hand area knowledge, Top DJÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s, Hosted Signature Events to name a few) normally donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t cost you anything additional, and in many cases, an Adults Only trip with VacationParties.com is even less than booking directly or with other groups!', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(21, 'Do you offer airfare?', 'We are happy to quote and book your airfare, no matter which package or destination you choose. Just ask one of our amazing Personal Travel Specialists for assistance. ', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(22, 'Do you offer special packages or discounts for special events/corporate/weddings/ groups?', 'Definitely!  Whatever the occasion, whatever your needs, just contact one of our Personal Travel Specialists for details, pricing, and a customized quote. You can even earn $50 Vacation Parties Travel Dollars for each booking you refer. So if youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re interested in putting a group together and referring them to VacationParties.com for their travel needs, you could easily earn a FREE vacation! \r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(8, 'Am I safe as a Single Girl on one of your vacations? ', 'Yes, we have several single ladies that come on our trips and have a great experience. We have some great testimonials that you can review on the testimonials tab on the home page.', 1, '2013-08-12'),
(9, 'Do I need Medical/Trip Insurance? ', 'Medical insurance is not required however strongly recommended. Most resorts have a Nurse on site and can call in a doctor when necessary, however the bill can quickly add up starting at 150.00US just to see the nurse. It can be something as little as a sting by a Jellyfish or even a broken leg, the reality is ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…â€œshit happensÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã‚? and you should always be prepared. As for Trip insurance, again, we have had clientÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢s trips impacted by a family tragedy and they were able to claim back their entire cost of the vacation. For the cost of trip insurance it is well worth the investment.', 1, '2013-08-12'),
(20, 'Do you offer transfers from the airport?', 'Yes we do! We are happy to arrange round-trip transfers to your resort/hotel and simply add it to your reservation. There are no separate bills or last-minute fees, allowing you to focus on your vacation party experience and leave the details to us.\r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(11, 'What is an All Inclusive Vacation mean? ', 'Simply that there is no need for you to walk around with money. Your food, alcohol some water sports (depending on resort) theme nights, and entertainment is all included in your hotel package. Tipping is also not required.', 1, '2013-08-12'),
(18, 'Do I have to travel with a group?', 'Of course not! We offer customizable vacations all over the world for couples, individuals and corporate group travelers who are looking to benefit from our first-hand knowledge of the best Adults-Only resorts, cruises, and destinations. WeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll even offer to research the best possible dates for your trip, based on resort, local, and group events.', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(16, 'Who are the people behind VacationParties.com?', 'Founded seven years ago by Darlene (Lady Dee) and Sarge Rhoden, VacationParties.com has grown to include an amazing network of staff and volunteers committed to the future of Adults Only Travel. Our Entire VacationParties.com Team strongly believes in gaining your trust before gaining your business and handles every inquiry and booking with discretion and integrity. Get to know our Team Members by visiting our ***Staff Bio Page***. ', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(17, 'Why is it better to travel with VacationParties.com than by ourselves?', 'If youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ve ever traveled to another country, you know that it can often be challenging to navigate the area and approach other people. When you travel with VacationParties.com, you receive the benefits of our extensive knowledge and experience of the Adults Only and Clothing Optional travel industry. WeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ve been there, we know what to do, where to go, and how to get the most out of your experience (and your dollar). We specialize in organizing Group Events and are famous for our VIP check-in, gift bags, ice-breaker events, guided tours and on-site assistance. Even if our group/event dates donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t work with your schedule and we arenÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t able to be there to personally host you, we can still help you find a resort that suits your needs and research other events/groups traveling on the same dates. WeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll also use our established relationships with the best Adults Only resorts to negotiate the most competitive rate possible. ', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(23, 'Do you offer packages to those outside of the United States/Canada?', 'Definitely! VacationParties.com is privileged to have clients from all over the world traveling with us, with some as far away as Brazil, Europe, South Africa, and Australia. We offer packages worldwide and our extremely knowledgeable staff can assist with booking airfare from airports all over the globe.\r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(24, 'How do I book?', 'The VacationParties.com ***Online Reservation System*** is simple, secure, and user-friendly; making it a hassle free experience that leaves you with nothing to do but look forward to your vacation! You can also email us Reservations@VacationParties.com or call us, toll free, at 800.458.2099 to speak with one of our Personal Travel Specialists. ', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(25, 'Do I have to leave on a specific date or can I choose my own travel dates?', 'Most Signature Events are set for specific dates, but we can certainly extend or customize to include any dates before or after the event itself to maximize your vacation experience. Those who travel without a group can certainly choose their own travel dates (subject to resort availability). If youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re unsure when youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re looking to travel, our Personal Travel Specialists will be happy to provide the best times for each region/country based on their weather and tourist/event seasons. ', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(26, 'What happens if I need to change my travel dates?', 'One of the many advantages with booking with VacationParties.com is the flexibility we offer when booking additional days or changing dates. WeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re happy to assist you with any changes or extensions (subject to availability) and also with updating your flight information (please note that most major airlines will charge a set change fee and any difference in airfare rates.)', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(27, 'How do I know about the Theme Nights, Parties, and Excursions offered on my trip?', 'Our Signature Event itineraries are posted on the Event Page (subject to change) and finalized itineraries will be emailed 2 weeks prior to travel date. For those not traveling with a Signature Group, there is also a list of resort-specific Themes and Activities located on the Resort Page where you can view their amenities and entertainment offerings. \r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(28, 'If the resort I choose is Ã¢â‚¬Å“clothing-optionalÃ¢â‚¬Â, do I have to be nude?', 'Certainly Not! While we do offer nudist vacations where nudity is required, we also offer clothing-optional resorts. These resorts take the personal comfort of their guests very seriously by providing clearly designated Ã¢â‚¬Å“nude or toplessÃ¢â‚¬Â areas. This gives you the option to enjoy the liberating and exotic Adults-Only atmosphere these resorts provide while keeping covered up. \r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(29, 'What payment options do you accept? ', 'We accept all major credit cards, personal/business checks (If more than 60 days out from date of travel), and direct deposits.\r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(30, 'Do you offer payment plans?', 'Absolutely! Our Famous Payment Plan options allow you up FOUR installments to pay off your vacations. The number and amount of installments offered will depend on the date of travel and any Airfare must be paid in full at time of booking. \r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(31, 'What are your cancellation/refund policies?', 'For details on our cancelation and refund policies, please see our ***Terms of Service***.\r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(32, 'How can I protect myself if I need to cancel my trip due to an emergency?', 'For extra flexibility and peace of mind, we recommend ***Travel insurance***. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s more cost-effective than you might think and there are multiple plans and layers of protection to choose from.\r\n', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(33, 'Do you offer an affiliate/partner program?', 'Definitely! We offer Cash Referral programs, Affiliate Link programs, and our world-renowned Travel Reseller Program. Check out or ***Vacation Affiliate Network Resource Page*** for more information or to get started today!', 1, '2014-08-01'),
(34, 'How do I get the best price?', 'Here at VacationParties.com, we donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t compete on price, we compete on value. We are not here to provide the cheapest anything, but to provide the best of everything. Our mission is to give you the most value and WOW! Factor for your dollar. Even with this goal in mind, our prices are often LESS than other travel agencies and even the resorts themselves!', 1, '2014-08-01');
