(4, 'Events', 0, 'events', '', '<p>Vacation parties are what vacationparties.com is all about. We are committed to helping you find the best holiday experiences for you and your friends or partner. All events listed on our site are hosted and organized by credible agencies and promoters, whom we have personally verified; to ensure you our valued clients enjoy the best possible experiences.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nOur website offers a variety of holiday events. All events are for &ldquo;adults only,&rdquo; meaning anyone over the age of 18 can book and attend our adults only vacation parties. Some events may require you to be older than 21, and the details of those events will specify exactly that.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhether you are looking for a party in Europe during the summer, if you are looking to experience one of the many clothing optional resort parties on our site or you are looking for that perfect weekend party get away, regardless of what your interest maybe, we have an event that is perfect for you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Inside The Adults Only Experience....Ã¢â‚¬Â¨</strong>Ã¢â‚¬Â¨<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWe love kids. Especially our own. However, we must admit that sometime we want to be kids ourselves and it is hard to do so when children are alone.<br />\r\nThis is why we have adult&rsquo;s only vacations. Not because we hate children, but because we would hate if the children saw how we really behave when they are not there. Every adult needs to have this experience. Especially if you are in a relationship.&nbsp;Ã¢â‚¬Â¨Ã¢â‚¬Â¨<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nAt Vacationparties.com, we specialize in adult&rsquo;s only tours and adult vacations, from clothing option resort parties to, party tours across Europe and Asia. On these vacations, you get to re-kindle those free-spirited teenage or college years where the only thing you cared about was having fun. This Kind of behave all the time can be somewhat reckless, but for a week or two on vacation