(9, 'FAQ', 0, 'faq', 'FAQ', '<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: Why AVP (Adult Vacation parties)? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id="para1">\r\n	A: With anyone of our AVP signature events, you can be guaranteed a good time! Starting with quality entertainers, our own Dj&rsquo;s, Unique concepts and theme nights, VIP check in service on arrival where the AVP team is there to meet n greet you with goodie bags, and another feature that makes us so different is our Famous Payment Plan options. That&rsquo;s right, we offer our guests up to FOUR installments to pay off their vacations. (depending on time of booking of course) Our clients love this feature. By the time you know it, your trip is paid for and you feel no pain ;)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: What are the benefits of booking with a Group?</strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="para1" id="para2">\r\n	A: One of the best benefits to booking with a group is that the resorts make the groups their Top Priorities. Which includes hotel entertainment and theme nights. Even the itineraries are changed to reflect that of the group. Flexibility with check in and check out dates and group package rates are usually better than what you can find on your own. So why feel left out, join a group and you will make the best of friends!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: Do I have to be Naked? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="para1" id="para2">\r\n	A: Many of the Resorts we take over are &ldquo;clothing optional&rdquo; which means it a choice. If you are comfortable and want to go naked, feel free, however you can also be Topless or not naked at all. And for these resorts there is no nudity in the Dining areas. The only time Nudity is required is on a Nudist Resort, which of course you would be aware of at time of booking.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: Are Transfers to and from the resort included? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="para1" id="para2">\r\n	A: Each resort if different. For Hedonism resorts, all transfer are included in your Hotel package. We will always inform you of transfer fees if any, and have them arranged on your behalf.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: What about the Flights? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="para1" id="para2">\r\n	A: With today&rsquo;s technology such as the Internet, and frequent flyer or air miles points there are so many great options and flights for you to take advantage of without limitations. One great advantage to booking with us at AVP is that you get the flexibility of playing with your arrival and departure dates. This is also great for those who like to extend their vacations with us beyond our scheduled theme weeks. For those who request, we will be happy to help you find flights on your behalf.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: What is a &ldquo;lifestyle&rdquo; vacation? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="para1" id="para2">\r\n	A: A lifestyle vacation means that YOU are the star of the show. You get to make this vacation whatever you want it to be. Whether that means dressing sexy for theme nights, exploring your sexual boundaries, or even just people watching, no matter what, you are in a safe place to do so without judgment and /or pressure to do anything at all. So relax and come have some deserved fun!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: Am I safe as a Single Girl on one of your vacations? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id="para2">\r\n	A: Yes, we have several single ladies that come on our trips and have a great experience. We have some great testimonials that you can review on the testimonials tab on the home page.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: Do I need Medical/Trip Insurance? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id="para2">\r\n	A: Medical insurance is not required however strongly recommended. Most resorts have a Nurse on site and can call in a doctor when necessary, however the bill can quickly add up starting at 150.00US just to see the nurse. It can be something as little as a sting by a Jellyfish or even a broken leg, the reality is &ldquo;shit happens&rdquo; and you should always be prepared. As for Trip insurance, again, we have had client&rsquo;s trips impacted by a family tragedy and they were able to claim back their entire cost of the vacation. For the cost of trip insurance it is well worth the investment.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: What about emergency contact information?</strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id="para2">\r\n	A: A very Special feature that we have added to all our &ldquo;Signature&rdquo; events is a number to our Direct cell phones that you can leave with your family should they need to find you, they can call us and we will locate you on the property and you can make a FREE call home. So no need to walk with the cell phones, enjoy yourself, we got you covered! Oh and we will even pretend your staying at Sandals lol ;)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q: What is an All Inclusive Vacation mean? </strong></p>\r\n<div style="clear:both; height:1px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id="para2">\r\n	A: Simply that there is no need for you to walk around with money. Your food, alcohol some water sports (depending on resort) theme nights, and entertainment is all included in your hotel package. Tipping is also not required.</p>', '', 'FAQ -- Adult Vacation Parties', NULL, 'FAQ -- Adult Vacation Parties', 'FAQ -- Adult Vacation Parties', '2013-01-06 03:09:22', 0),
