(19, 'Accomodation', 0, 'accomodation', 'Accomodation', '<p>All Rates displayed are per person, based on two people staying in a room. For hotels that allow singles, a single room premium of 50% of the total charge will be required if you wish to have the room to yourself. If not you can do a single-to-share option at the per person double occupancy cost. &nbsp;This hotel&nbsp;is all inclusive meaning, all meals, drinks, premium liquor and some watersports activites are included in the price. Hotel amenties generally include, bars, restaurants,night clubs, pools and Jacuzzi tubs. Spa facilities will attract an additional cost. Room prices does not include airfare nor resort transfers. We will arrange your resort transfers separately, once we have your flight details confirmed. If you would like us to help you arrange flights, please indicate when completing the reservation form.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '-1', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
