(21, 'AVP Host', 0, 'host', 'AVP Host', '<p>We are Ladydee and Sarge, your AVP hosts. We are committed to bringing quality events and service to the community of open-minded adults, who are looking to have fun outside of the everyday, conventional, mundane activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a young couple promoting and hosting lifestyle events, we bring a fresh perspective to what quality entertainment and sexy events are all about. We represent the new generation of open-mindedness and we strive to deliver events that appeal to the couples and adults of the 21<sup>st</sup> century looking to add spice and adventure to their lives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are young, energetic, but by no means inexperienced as we have been successfully promoting and hosting events in the lifestyle community for over six years and currently run one of the biggest resort take-over groups in the lifestyle community.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are extremely passionate about what we do. We get great joy out of meeting new people and helping them discover things about themselves that they never knew existed. We do this not just as a job, but for the satisfaction we get from watching others evolve through there comfort levels and embrace freedom and sexuality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The quality of our events are important to us, so that is why all of our Signature Events are personally hosted by us, as we want to be personally accountable to each person that attend our events, making sure they have a great experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We love travelling, dancing, partying and being sexy, but helping people experience freedom and fantasy is what we live for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite you all to join us on one of our vacation parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, 'AVP Host', 'Your Hosts', 'A Message From Your Adult Vacation Parties Host', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
