(25, 'Affiliate Terms & Conditions For Affiliate', 0, 'affiliate-tnc', 'Terms & Conditions', '<h3><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">The Affiliate partners participation agreement of&nbsp;Sunset Destinations and Adult Tours Inc, owner and operater of adultvacationparties.com,&nbsp;hereinafter referred to as <strong>&ldquo;AVP&rdquo; </strong>TICO REG# 50018479, IATA #965 343 33, Ã¢â‚¬Â¨30 Eglinton Avenue WestÃ¢â‚¬Â¨ Unit # C-12 Mississauga, On L5R 3E7<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo participate in the AVP Affiliate Program, you must agree to the following:<br />\r\nThis Affiliate Agreement contains the complete terms and conditions between AVP and the Affiliate, regarding your application to participate as an affiliate of AVP, and the establishment of links from your website to our website, www.adultvacationparties.com, in exchange for a commission of, $80 (US or CDN) for all FIT (Frequent individual Travel) bookings and 5% per couple commission for all qualified purchase within a group contract.<br />\r\nBY SUBMITTING AN APPLICATION TO JOIN OR BY PARTICIPATING IN THE AVP AFFILIATE PROGRAM, YOU ARE CONFIRMING THAT YOU HAVE READ THIS AGREEMENT AND AGREE TO BE BOUND BY ITS TERMS AND CONDITIONS AS DESCRIBED BELOW:<br />\r\nAVP Affiliate Agreement Definitions<br />\r\n&quot;You&quot;, &quot;Affiliate(s)&quot; - the business, individual or entity applying for participation in the Affiliate Program, or that displays our products, services and/or promotions on its website and/or through offline<br />\r\n<img src="file://localhost/Users/Sargemac/Library/Caches/TemporaryItems/msoclip/0/clip_image002.png" style="height:3px; width:184px" />&nbsp;<img src="file://localhost/Users/Sargemac/Library/Caches/TemporaryItems/msoclip/0/clip_image004.png" style="height:3px; width:209px" />&nbsp;<img src="file://localhost/Users/Sargemac/Library/Caches/TemporaryItems/msoclip/0/clip_image006.png" style="height:3px; width:42px" />&nbsp;<img src="file://localhost/Users/Sargemac/Library/Caches/TemporaryItems/msoclip/0/clip_image008.png" style="height:3px; width:92px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nRepresentation through the affiliate tracking code in exchange for receiving remuneration from AVP for sales resulting from such display.<br />\r\nDEFINITIONS:<br />\r\n&quot;Affiliate Website&quot; - the Affiliate&#39;s Internet site which displays AVP Products and Services and/or promotions.<br />\r\n&quot;AVP Products and Services&quot; &ndash; Online travel services, which includes, hotel reservations, cruise reservations, trip insurance and other travel related products.<br />\r\n&quot;Commission Fees&quot; or &quot;Commissions&quot; - Under the Affiliate Program, subject to the terms hereof, you will be paid a Commission Fee for each Qualified Purchase by a Customer that you refer to AVP under and in accordance with this Agreement within 15 days after the client has paid in full and passed cancelation period.<br />\r\n&quot;Qualified Purchase&quot; - a sale of AVP Products and Services by AVP that is not cancelled or is purchased after the 45 day full cancellation penalty period.<br />\r\n&quot;Referred Customer&quot; - each new and unique customer referred from Affiliate through the travel page setup on affiliates site, using the tracking code provided by or approved by AVP, which meets the criteria set forth.<br />\r\n&quot;Registration Form&quot; - any and all order forms, Registration Forms, or other signup or acceptance form (whether online, paper, fax, or otherwise) submitted by you or, as applicable, the Referred Customer to make a Qualified Purchase.<br />\r\nRequirements: <strong>Enrollment in the Affiliate Network</strong><br />\r\nTo begin the enrollment process, you must first read carefully and check mark the box below, confirming you have read and agreed with all terms within. Your enrollment may be terminated if for any reason you use the name of AVP or Sunset Destinations in a manner that is misleading to the consumers and considered to be unlawful or put in jeopardy the licensing and good standings of AVP with the Travel Industry council.<br />\r\nOnce registration is completed and approved, you will now have access to an API (Application Programming Interface) code, that you can now copy and paste into a travel page you have created on your current website. <u>This code will allow your visitors to book AVP events and travel, through your website without ever leaving your site.</u> Your login area will allow you track all qualified purchases and commissions earned. Including commission due dates.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; <strong>Promotion of Our Affiliate Relationship</strong><br />\r\nIf you agree to become an affiliate, AVP will be responsible for making available to you, a variety of images, links and text that should be used for promoting our products and services. In keeping with travel industry regulations, it is understood that it be made clear on your website that <u>travel services are provided by and will be managed by adultvacationparties.com, owned and operated by Sunset Destinations and Adult Tours</u>, licensed travel provider in North America. Should the Affiliate want to use marketing material other then what is provided by AVP for marketing of travel, or travel related services, they must first be approved by AVP.<br />\r\nAll websites, brochures or any other form of marketing material selling travel, must contain, the company name, logo, and licensing information of AVP.<br />\r\nAVP will be responsible for all hotel contracts, negotiations of contracts setting prices and creating the material to be used to promote all travel related services offered by Affiliates. Affiliates are not allowed to collect client funds, set prices or offer discounts on behalf of AVP. All funds for travel or travel related services according to the Travel industry council should be held in a trust account to be provided by Sunset Destinations and Adult Tours and AVP for the protection of the consumer.<br />\r\n<strong>PROPERTY RIGHTS:</strong><br />\r\nAll Links may be modified and/or expanded from time to time throughout the term of this Agreement pursuant to the mutual agreement of the parties hereto. You are not allowed to post any refunds, credits or discounts, or other content concerning AVP, unless AVP has given you prior written permission in each instance. Affiliates may only use coupons and discounts that are provided exclusively through the Affiliate Program using banners and links. Each Link connecting users of your site to the pertinent area of our site will in no way alter the look, feel, or functionality of our site. Any violations of the terms surrounding links, coupons, refunds, credits or discounts shall constitute a material breach of this Agreement, and may result in your termination from the program or withholding of Commissions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>ORDER PROCESSING:</strong><br />\r\nOrders will be processed through affiliates travel page that is created using the API code provided by AVP. This will allow clients to process their order through Affiliate websites, but using the AVP reservation system. We reserve the right, in our sole discretion, to reject orders that do not comply with certain requirements that we may establish from time to time. All aspects of order processing and fulfillment, including AVP service, cancellation, processing, refunds and payment processing will be our responsibility. We will track the Qualified Purchases generated by your website and will make this information available to you through the affiliate tracking system. To permit accurate tracking, reporting, and Commission accrual, you must ensure that the Links between your website and our website are properly formatted.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>COMMISSION DETERMINATION:</strong><br />\r\nUnder the Affiliate Program, you will be paid a Commission Fee for each Qualified Purchase by a Customer that you refer to AVP under and in accordance with the terms of this Agreement. Each Referred Customer and each Qualified Purchase must meet the following criteria<br />\r\n<strong>CRITERIA:</strong><br />\r\nEach Referred Customer must be a new Customer to AVP and must register by completing and submitting the Registration Form using a valid and unique account and billing information.<br />\r\nEach Referred Customer must make a Qualified Purchase, and provide a valid payment for the purchased Products or Services. To generate a Commission Fee for you, each Referred Customers must be up-to-date in all payments at the time the Commission Fees are processed and not have been subject to a refund, credit, cancellation, suspension or chargeback.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nService, Acceptable Use Policy and other policies that are active at the time the Commission Fees are processed.</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Commissions will only be paid after the customer has paid in full, travelled or past the 45 day no cancellation period.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Commission Fees and Payments: Ã¢â‚¬Â¨</strong>Subject to the terms of this Agreement, we will pay a Commission Fee equal of $80 per double occupancy for each booking of minimum 5 fully paid nights or more for all FIT bookings. We will pay 5% per booking per double occupancy for all group bookings of 5 fully paid nights or more. Ã¢â‚¬Â¨Bookings for singles will be paid at 40% of the above-mentioned commissions. Commissions will be paid out after the client&rsquo;s trip has been paid in full to the resort and they can no longer cancel. The total commissions will be paid once per month for the total number of qualified customers.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Payment Forms/Types: Ã¢â‚¬Â¨</strong>Commissions can be paid via; check, wire transfers, PayPal or direct deposits. Please notify in writing of your preferred method of payment</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">AVP is not responsible for any third-party fees charged by PayPal, bank or other financial institute used to receive Affiliate Commission Fees. You can update or change desired payment form at any time by sending us an email with the new payment information. Changes to desired payment form may take up to two payout cycles to take affect. AVP, in its sole discretion, reserves the right to modify the terms of this Commission payment method or schedule at any time.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Obligations Regarding Your Affiliates Travel Page</strong> AVP will be responsible for the development and maintenance of all travel related services provided through the API code. Affiliates are responsible for setting up the travel page on their website that will display AVP&rsquo;s products and services through the affiliate code provide. &nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp;<br />\r\nOur website; the accuracy and propriety of materials posted on Affiliates site (including, but not limited to, all materials related to AVP Products and Services); ensuring that materials posted on Affiliates site, does not violate or infringe upon the rights of any third party and are not libelous or otherwise illegal. All postings and updates must be jointly approved before posting.<br />\r\nWe have the right in our sole discretion to monitor signups through your site at any time and from time to time to determine if you are in compliance with the terms of this Agreement. If you are not in compliance AVP may terminate this Agreement immediately.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>AVP Responsibilities: </strong>We will be responsible for providing all information necessary to allow you to make appropriate Links from Your site to our site. AVP