(27, 'Affiliate', 0, 'affiliate-advertisement', 'Affiliate', 'Add a new revenue stream to your current website by signing up for the AVP affiliate program. By becoming an affiliate with AVP, you get a full travel page added to your site where visitors can, view travel events and resort details, complete an online booking through the AVP system, but never leave your website. All reservations made on our affiliate site will be managed by adultvacationparties.com, but you earn a commission every time a booking is completed through your affiliate site.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nSigning Up&hellip;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nSigning up is very simple. Click on the registration button, and complete the online form. Once form is completed, you will now be registered and admin will review your application. Once your application is approved, you will receive an email to login to your management profile, where you can now copy your API (Application Programming Interface) code, paste it into a travel page that you have created on your site, and visitors will now be able to view all AVP&rsquo;s events (Resorts and Cruises coming soon) through your website. You can track your commissions by logging into your management area.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nAffiliate travel pages will be updated through the AVP system so you do not need to worry about managing the page. All you have to do is, sign up, copy the code, and start earning commission when your visitors book travel.', NULL, 'Affiliate', 'affiliate-1', 'Affiliate', 'Affiliate', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(28, 'Customer Loyalty Program', 0, 'loyalty-advertisement', 'Customer Loyalty Program', 'Get cash back every time you book a trip with AVP. Introducing AVP&rsquo;s new preferred customers program, where you will now earn travel points every time you book travel through AVP. Not only will you earn points from booking your own travel, refer a friend to book travel with us and earn points through them booking as well. Manage your reservations and payments through your preferred customer profile and save time.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nOnce you book your first trip with AVP, you will become a preferred customer, and your login information will be sent your email so you can start tracking your rewards, manage your reservations, refer friends to earn points, and redeem your reward points for future travel.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nBook a trip now and start earning points.', NULL, 'Customer Loyalty Program', 'customer-loyalty-program', 'Customer Loyalty Program', 'Customer Loyalty Program', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
