(20, 408, 'Hedonism II', 'Hedonism | Hedonism II | Hedonism Resorts | Negril Jamaica Vacations', '<h1><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Hedonism Resort&nbsp;Jamaica</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Sleep in. Stay up late. Give up counting calories. Have a drink before noon. Give up mineral water. Dine in shorts. Talk to strangers. Don&rsquo;t make your bed. Go skinny dipping. Don&rsquo;t call your mother. Let your hair down. Don&rsquo;t pay for anything. Don&rsquo;t leave a tip. But above all- be your beautiful, uninhibited self at the spectacular&nbsp;<strong>Hedonism Resort Jamaica</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located in the fabulous Negril, Jamaica, Hedonism is a playground for your inner child and nourishment for the mind, body, spirit and soul. At the&nbsp;<strong>Hedonism II</strong>, a world of delight and excitement awaits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pleasure comes in many forms, and at the Hedonism Resort you decide where your desires lead you. Absolutely everything is included in one upfront price, so the only thing you&#39;ll have to think about is what fantasy to fulfil next. At the all-inclusive Hedonism, you won&#39;t be bothered with paying for beverages or food, you can drink and dine to your heart&#39;s content and stay focused on more important things- like what indulgent activity you&#39;ll be enjoying soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:small">Hedonism II</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Hedonism 2 is the first of its kind and this adults-only utopia has become the epitome of quality and the standard to which all other clothing-optional resorts aspire. Though many resorts of this category have been established, Hedonism still offers entertainment and recreation that&#39;s hard to come by. The Hedonism Resort Jamaica awaits your arrival and urges you to enter the Hedonism world of amusement and bliss. Just as its name implies, the Hedonism 2 is an atmosphere of total euphoria and complete contentment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Book your trip to the Hedonism today and turn your wildest dreams into incredible realities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:small">Book Hedonism to Get More You Expect From Your Beach Vacations</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enter to a new world of freedom and joy. Do everything and anything you want. Stay up late. Forget about your diet. Drink your wine for lunch. Forget mineral water. Wear less and show everything. Talk to strangers. Leave your room messy. Dive in the beaches naked. Don&rsquo;t pay for anything. Be anything and everything you want and Hedonism Resorts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hedonism is a sandbox for your inner child, nourishment for the mind, body, spirit and soul. Pleasure comes in many forms. Book Hedonism now and relieve your inner childhood. Forget tipping them just indulge you to pleasure and delight.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:small">Experience it deeper and wilder.&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Let your inner child wonder. Release your primal urge to let go. Unwind and simply be free. Hedonism II is the perfect vacation leisure pleasure for adults. Interesting twists such as a pool table in the pool and a nude pool with swim-up bar make this place definitely adults only. Different events and themed entertainment also happens at Hedonism II.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;This is what happens when you combine sandy beaches and open-minded people, hedonism vacations. Open yourself and nourish your mind and body while relaxing in different pleasurable forms while on vacation. You&rsquo;ll be tanned and relaxed. And at times you&rsquo;ll find yourself smiling for no reason whatsoever. Hedonism, there&rsquo;s nothing else on earth quite like it. Get back to the real world, renewed and fresh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h5><span style="font-size:small">Hedonism Negril is an exclusive resort for adults.&nbsp;</span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Ages from 18 below are not allowed and considered children. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s a vacation party for adults either singles or couples. While here, you can enjoy the many pools (some with swim-up pool bars) and Jacuzzis, along with spa services and a fitness center. There are many different activities and forms of entertainment at Hedonism Specials, and Adult Vacation Parties offers a look at what&#39;s going on when. You can choose to have your trip coincide with one of these fun couples or singles themed weeks or just simply laze around the hotel with your partner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uniquely located on the tip of one of Jamaica&#39;s most legendary Beaches on the Western point of the Island called Negril, This beautifully landscaped all-inclusive resort centers around two stretches of sandy beach: One nude and one none nude to clothing optional. This is a big part of what makes the spirit of Hedonism III so enjoyable, like the beaches so are the Clientele diverse.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hedonism resorts could really be called the Disney world for Adult. With the three restaurants and two beach grills one prude and one nude, there is 24 hour food service the last being after midnight snacks that works fine, as there is also a Fitness center available 24 hours as well. The resort also offers best deals on Spa Facilities, 5 bars including a highly energized piano bar, along with a night club. 280 rooms with Suites with their own patio Jacuzzi&rsquo;s!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>WATER SPORTS</strong><br />\r\nIf it turns you on, do it. Hedonism boasts one of Jamaica&rsquo;s most complete aquatic centers, featuring top-of-the-line equipment and professional instruction at no additional charge. With just a few quick lessons, you&rsquo;ll be able to take to the sea with style.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our aquatics center is open from 9:00am to 5:00pm and includes some of the following activities:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Scuba diving (see below)</li>\r\n	<li>Water-skiing</li>\r\n	<li>Hobie cat</li>\r\n	<li>Windsurfing school</li>\r\n	<li>Sunfish</li>\r\n	<li>Sailing</li>\r\n	<li>Snorkeling</li>\r\n	<li>Kayaks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>By now you&rsquo;ve heard that Hedonism II is located on one of Jamaica&rsquo;s most spectacular beaches. This water wonderland also features:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Jacuzzis (on the Prude side)</li>\r\n	<li>Jacuzzis (on the Nude side)</li>\r\n	<li>Three (3) freshwater pools</li>\r\n	<li>Swim-up pool bar (on the Prude side)</li>\r\n	<li>Swim-up pool bar (on the Nude side)</li>\r\n	<li>Cascading plunge pools</li>\r\n	<li>Waterslide</li>\r\n	<li>Beachfront pool</li>\r\n	<li>&amp; more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Entertainment is arguably the heart of Hedonism. From live music and entertainment to a world-famous nightclub, we&rsquo;ve got you covered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NIGHTLY ENTERTAINMENT</strong><br />\r\nEnjoy live entertainment and resident bands on our center stage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy our live band from 8:30pm &ndash; 12:00am every night (except Fridays) on our center stage in the Main Terrace Dining room.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shows</strong><br />\r\nPerformers and floor shows every night in the open-air entertainment area of the Main Terrace as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>THEME NIGHTS</strong><br />\r\nEvery night at Hedonism is a new party. Live out your fantasies at our exciting costume and theme night parties. Theme Nights</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Monday</strong><br />\r\nSEXY PIRATES &amp; BOOTYÃ¢â‚¬Â¨Aaaaaargh!! Jamaican Colors with Sexy Booty Shorts and Hot Pirates &amp; Wenches</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tuesday</strong><br />\r\nPAJAMAS &amp; PASTIESÃ¢â‚¬Â¨Tease &amp; Tempt In Lustful Pajamas &amp; Pasties, the Sexiest Party of the Week</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wednesday</strong><br />\r\nFETISH FANTASYÃ¢â‚¬Â¨Expose Your Alter Ego &amp; Fetish in an Intoxicating Atmosphere of Fantasy Fashion Frenzy</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Thursday</strong><br />\r\nBLACK &amp; WHITE STARLIGHT NIGHTÃ¢â‚¬Â¨The Stars Shine Bright In the Sexiest Black &amp; White Costumes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Friday</strong><br />\r\nROCKING ROCK STARS Dress As Your Favorite Rock Idol and Party Like A Rock Star Saturday MASKPARADEDoll Yourselves Up But Don&rsquo;t Forget to Add Your Special Mystery Mask to the Sexy Ensemble</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sunday</strong><br />\r\nNAUGHTY SCHOOL REUNIONÃ¢â‚¬Â¨Dress to Impress As A Sexy School Girl, Nerd, Principal Or Cheerleader Activities, times and locations are all subject to change without notice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BARS</strong><br />\r\nFrom live music and entertainment to a world-famous hip nightclub, we&rsquo;ve got you covered. Click to learn more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DAILY ACTIVITIES</strong><br />\r\nJust because the sun comes up, doesn&rsquo;t mean the parties over. Hedonism offers plenty of daytime activities to keep you busy.</p>\r\n', 'H2-1271.jpg', '', '', 1, 1, 'hedonism', 'Turn your fantasies into realities at the Hedonism Resort Jamaica.A world of sheer indulgence and pleasure at the inclusive Hedonism I & II. Negril vacation.', 'Hedonism, Hedonism II, Hedonism Resort, Hedonism Resorts, Hedonism Jamaica', '2013-09-02 09:37:37', 1, 15, 110, 'Hedonism II is a clothing optional adults only resort, for both couples and singles located in Negril, Jamaica. The resort has both a Nude and Clothing optional beach, offer great entertainment and is located on the world famous Seven Mile White Sand Beach in Negril. Hedonism is known for it''s wild nightlife and party atmosphere. It is one of the world''s first clothing optional all-inclusive resorts.', 'Hedonism Resort', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(24, 0, 'Temptation Resort Cancun', 'Temptation Resort | Temptation Cancun | Temptation Resort and Spa | Temptation Resort Cancun', '<p><strong><em>Temptation Resort and Spa</em></strong>, formerly Blue Bay Getaway Spa, features an exciting concept in all inclusive resort living.&nbsp; The resort offers sexy open-minded atmosphere that allows you to enjoy a unique fantasy vacation experience.&nbsp; The hotel entertainment staff, affectionately called &quot;Temptation Cast&quot;, organizes a variety of adult-oriented games and contests with naughty overtones.&nbsp; This all-inclusive vacation features unique takes on even exercise. The Sensual Fitness program for women includes classes in lap and pole dancing, exotic moves and more.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong><em>Temptation Resort</em></strong> is conveniently located on the fourteen Mile-long Island between the hotel zone&#39;s &quot;Party Central&quot; and downtown Cancun. Guests arriving into Cancun International Airport will travel just 20 short minutes to Temptation Resort &amp; Spa.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nBoth singles and couples over the age of 21 are allowed at Temptations Resort. The ongoing party atmosphere provides a contemporary take on the all-inclusive holiday. A hip vibe is the hallmark of this beachfront resort.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>The Restaurants</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong><em>Temptation Resort and Spa </em></strong>boasts of its excellent 24-hour service, world-class restaurants, live entertainment and fun filled activities. Enjoy a wide variety of international cuisine at El Embarcadero as it changes its menu themes every night. Get that exotic feeling while dining at Village Wok as it serves authentic Asian cuisine. Have a romantic gourmet Italian dinner at IL Piacere and Caribbean specialties at Bella vista. The premiere party and dining place is at Margarita&#39;s snack bar &amp; Grill and Paty&#39;O Lounge.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Temptation Resort and Spa</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Spa Sensations at <strong><em>Temptation Resort</em></strong>, offers a chic, sensual and relaxing atmosphere that is highlighted with rich fabrics, metallic colors and textured wall coverings that along with crystal accents, modern chandeliers, and soft lighting perfectly set the mood for a pampering day. One relaxation room equipped with oversize furniture and two chaise lounges, a tea and snack station; four private treatment rooms and even a couple&#39;s treatment room are the spaces where you will experience comfort and wellness. Two large, glass-tiled Jacuzzis set beneath a softly illuminated ceiling, and Co-ed Swedish Saunas are also available. Newly furnished male and female changing areas with steam rooms, saunas, lockers, bathrooms and showers add to the comfort of this fascinating spot of the resort<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>The Pool&hellip;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nIf you are at <strong><em>Temptation Cancun</em></strong> and you are looking for a little bit of daytime adventure, the main pool is the place to be. It&rsquo;s right next to the ocean and beach, so you can do the pool, or do the beach. Bartenders at the beachfront palapa serve up cocktails with a smile, the hotel DJ spins upbeat music and the entertainment staff lets you get involved, or just watch, as they put on daily shows<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>The Bars and Entertainment&hellip;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nBar options include a couple of swim-up bars, a sports bar and a highly popular patio bar that serves as the main meeting point in the evenings. The Nice Shoes Disco host nightly shows in the evening, ranging from Karaoke Night to sexy dancing shows to a lingerie show. Brief full nudity is allowed at some of the shows.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nAt Night the heart beat of <strong><em>Temptation Cancun</em></strong>, The Patty&rsquo; O Lounge, awaits you with mixes 