asy vacation experience. Enjoy topless pool and beach sunbathing at temptations, along with a very high-energy party atmosphere.', 'Temptation Resort Cancun', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(25, 0, 'Hidden Beach Resort', 'Hidden Beach Resort | Nudist | Mexico | Cancun Resort  Keywords: Hidden Beach Resort, Nudist Resort Mexico, Nudist Resort Cancun', '<p><strong>The Hidden Beach Resort Story</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hidden Beach Resort - Au Naturel Club is a brand new vacation product developed specifically for the needs of the nudism enthusiast. The idea for such a product was born out of a one-time weeklong nude vacation group, organized in conjunction with the first ever nude flight, Naked Air (May 2003).&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the huge interest and success of the first-ever nude flight, Hidden Beach Resorts decided to venture into this unique market niche as they spotted a gap in high quality nudist vacation products. They conducted extensive research in the clothing-optional market, surveyed nudist vacationers, and with the generous assistance of several market insiders, developed --from the ground up-- a concept for a luxurious vacation product designed specifically for the needs of nude vacationers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enter Hidden Beach Resort - Au Naturel Club, a 5 Star all-inclusive adults only nudist resort. Its setting, location and architecture were created to provide worry-free nude vacationing. A nudist could literally spend a week at this property without having to put on a single piece of clothing once. That&#39;s because the 42-room beachfront resort is totally secluded and private, prohibiting entrance and views to anyone but the resort guests and staff. Besides the public areas around the pool, beach and Jacuzzi, the resort offers nude dining at the all-inclusive restaurant, nude bars as well as a nude disco. The private beach is perfect for nude sunbathing and a variety of beach activities and fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h3>Sun on the rooftop,&nbsp;bubble in the hot tub, chill out in a Sky Palapa.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hidden Beach Resort is an all-inclusive, adults-only vacation destination on the Riviera Maya designed specifically for nudists. The 42 oceanfront suites provide an intimate environment where guests can feel comfortable clothing free, and enjoy the camaraderie of other nudists while sunning, dining and enjoying recreational activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This private hideaway features a rooftop sunning deck, swim-up bar, king-size beach beds, Sky Palapas, in-pool lounge chairs and a massive hot tub. All suites feature ocean views, a Jacuzzi for two and a king-size, pillow-top bed. There are swim-up suites and Dome suites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Luxury touches include waiter service at the pool and beach, beach massages, 24-hour room service, concierge service and private candlelight dinners on the beach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Guests enjoy nude dining, nude bars, the nude disco, and nude activities ranging from beach volleyball to morning yoga and evening theme parties. They may wear clothes if they choose. And there are more options (clothed) at El Dorado Seaside Suites next door.</p>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Daytime</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll thoroughly enjoy your time at Hidden Beach Resort, whether you want to get active in the sun or simply relax.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Night Time</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the evenings after leisurely meals, don&rsquo;t miss the nightly entertainment show of music and dance. Afterwards there&rsquo;s a party with a different theme each night<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Regional Tours</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re in search of exotic fish and coral, adrenalin thrills, cultural performances, water sports, nature or a glimpse into a mysterious ancient culture, you&rsquo;ll find it along Mexico&rsquo;s Riviera Maya. The concierge can help make arrangements.</p>\r\n', 'HBR_Beach0.jpg', '', '', NULL, 0, 'hidden-beach-resort', 'Hidden Beach Resort is an adults-only vacation destination on the Riviera Maya Mexico. Designed specifically for nudists. A concept for a luxurious vacation.', 'Hidden Beach Resort, Nude Beach, Nude Beach Mexico', '2013-09-07 00:00:00', 1, 12, 142, 'Enter Hidden Beach Resort - Au Naturel Club, a 5 Star all-inclusive adults only nudist resort. Its setting, location and architecture were created to provide worry-free nude vacationing. Hidden beach is located in Cancun, Mexico.', 'Hidden Beach Resort', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0);
