(26, 0, 'Caliente Tampa', 'Caliente Tampa | Nudist Resort | Resorts | Florida | USA', '<p>Caliente Tampa is a captivating blend of solitude, exhilaration and sizzle that is ideal for the seasoned naturist and first-time nudist alike.&nbsp; Inside Caliente Tampa, you will be pampered, wined, dined, and treated with world-class sensitivity you so richly deserve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beautifully appointed Villas, Condominiums, vacation Casitas&nbsp;and Hotel Suites&nbsp;will become your secluded home away from home for a stay that might last but a week or two, yet the memories will last a lifetime.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just outside your door, turquoise lagoons, a sapphire lake, sports and fitness facilities, tiki bars, decadent cuisine, and sumptuous&nbsp;<a href="https://calienteresorts.com/spa/" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">Spa Sereno</a>&nbsp;are just a few of the many opportunities that beckon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Things to do around our Tampa resort</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Beyond the beauty of Caliente Tampa, one of Florida&rsquo;s most progressive and dynamic metropolitan areas is within easy reach.&nbsp; With all its museums, professional sporting events, concert halls, challenging golf courses and world-class shopping destinations, Tampa Bay is one of the state&rsquo;s fastest-growing and friendliest regions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To the south is Ft. Desoto State Park, named the Best Beach in the United States in 2005 and the southernmost point to a wide variety of sugar-sand beaches stretching all along an area known to locals as &ldquo;The Suncoast&quot;.&nbsp; Many barrier islands dot the western Gulf coast as well, and attract some of the state&rsquo;s most diverse seabird populations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Gulf is also ideal for deep sea and backwater fishing, as are the Tampa Bay area&rsquo;s many freshwater lakes and rivers.&nbsp; To the east, Walt Disney World, Universal Studios, Sea World, Kennedy Space Center and other world renowned attractions await.&nbsp; Just pick a point on the compass and start exploring - wonderful adventures can be found around every corner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tampa Bay is also the site of numerous professional and pro-am golfing and tennis events throughout the year.&nbsp; For gaming of a different sort, there is the newly built Hard Rock Hotel and Cas, greyhound racing at Derby Lanes, and thoroughbred action at Tampa Bay Downs.</p>\r\n', '<h3>Clothing Optional Luxury</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You may not know it yet, but you are about to experience the most wonderful vacation you can imagine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bring your towels, hat and sunscreen then be ready to immerse yourself in relaxation, great conversation and nude recreation at its finest!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thoroughly indulge yourself at America&#39;s, if not the world&#39;s, most luxurious clothing optional resort; home of clothes-free fun all day and all night too!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow the links to learn more about our exceptional accommodations...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:rgb(85, 85, 94); font-family:tahoma,verdana,arial,serif; font-size:13px">Superior Hotel Rooms</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>First and Second floor accommodations perfectly located next to the resort amenities area.&nbsp; Each air-conditioned room includes a screened-in porch or balcony, providing a uniquely relaxing environment with views of the pool decks and sand volleyball courts!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our most popular weekend rental features a firm, king size Sealy Posturepedic mattress with 250 thread count poly cotton sheets, mini-refrigerator, microwave, satellite television, clock radio, sitting area with table, free local telephone service, corian top vanity, bathtub/shower combination, lush 18 oz. bath towels, coffee maker, hair dryer and our Caliente signature toiletries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check-in time for hotel rooms is 3pm or later and check-out time is 11am. Hotel rooms have a maximum occupancy of two adults and for your comfort, we do not allow pets in any of our rental units.</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; "><span style="color:rgb(85, 85, 94); font-family:tahoma,verdana,arial,serif; font-size:13px">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<h3>Private and Easily Accessible Cottages</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Located throughout the Casita Village are these air-conditioned, one bedroom cottages that feature a porch or screen room for leisure and outdoor relaxation!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These rentals are sunny, airy modern cottages with kitchen/living room combinations, satellite television, queen sleeper sofas, stereo, dining area, free local telephone service, refrigerator/freezer, electric range, microwave, dishwasher, coffee maker and small wares.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each Casita also features a full bath with bathtub/shower combination, Caliente signature toiletries, lush 18 oz. bath towels and queen bed with 250 thread count poly-cotton sheets. Casitas have a maximum occupancy of four persons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deluxe designated Casitas feature a room addition replacing the porch area and come with a DVD player. For your comfort, we do not allow pets or smoking in Casita rentals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Featuring At-Home Comfort &amp; Convenience</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>These spacious, individually decorated one and two-bedroom Condominiums are located throughout Caliente&rsquo;s beautiful residential community!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The well-appointed, first or second floor rentals feature fully equipped kitchens, living room, satellite television, VCR, free local telephone service and a dining area with sliding glass doors opening onto a screened-in porch or balcony for fresh breezes and your outdoor enjoyment!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our 800 square foot one-bedroom units have a full bath with bathtub/shower combination and a queen bed. Maximum occupancy of our one-bedroom Condominiums is four persons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our 1,200 square foot two-bedroom units feature two queen beds and have two full baths; the master bath having a toilet, bidet and an oversized walk-in shower. Maximum occupancy of our two bedroom Condominiums is six persons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most one and two-bedroom units offer a queen sleeper sofa and all feature lush 18 oz. bath towels, Caliente signature amenities and 250 thread count poly-cotton sheets. For your comfort, we do not allow pets in any of our rental units.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deluxe Condominiums feature a king bed in the master bedroom, 27&rdquo; or larger television, DVD player and washer and dryer. At this time, all of our Condominiums, Casitas and Villas are designated non-smoking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Ultimate In Decadent Luxury</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>These Richly Appointed, two story, 3 bedroom, two and a half bath town homes are just incredible! Each Villa has a two-car garage and 2,200 square feet of living space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features include free local telephone service, satellite television, poly-cotton 250 thread count sheets on all bedding, lush 18 oz. bath towels and Caliente&#39;s very own signature toiletries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" class="alignCenter pad05_bottom" src="https://calienteresorts.com/Site/images/tampa/villa_diningroom.jpg" style="border:0px; display:block; height:275px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; padding-bottom:5px; width:412px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the First Floor you will find a Half Bath, open fully equipped Kitchen with large breakfast bar, Dining Area and a huge Living Room with eight foot tall double sliding glass doors opening onto a large screened-in patio with a waterfront view.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" class="alignCenter pad05_bottom" src="https://calienteresorts.com/Site/images/tampa/villa_kitchen.jpg" style="border:0px; display:block; height:265px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; padding-bottom:5px; width:412px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Second Floor boasts a Master Bedroom to die for; the sliding glass doors open onto a screened-in balcony where you can enjoy wonderful Florida breezes and a serene view of the water!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The master bath is the final word in opulence, with a Jacuzzi tub, oversized enclosed glass walk-in shower, his and hers sinks, toilet and a bidet. Also found on the second floor is another full bath with bathtub &amp; shower combination, washer, dryer and two Additional Bedrooms each having a queen bed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum Occupancy for our villas is six persons and children are welcome. For your comfort, we do not allow pets in any of our rental units and at this time, all of our Casitas, Condominiums and Villas are designated non-smoking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Vacation Home</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine spending your next Caliente vacation in a fully equipped private vacation rental home right on (or very near) the Caliente Resort property!</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>What is a private vacation home rental?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Essentially, vacation home rentals are your home away from home - many times they&#39;re even better than your own home!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A vacation rental home is going on vacation but still having everything you have at home... fully equipped kitchens, well appointed baths, living rooms and dining rooms mean you&#39;re not cramped into a single small room!</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>What about the cost of renting a vacation home?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Vacation home rentals are usually more cost effective the more people you&nbsp; have, which make them perfect for a Caliente vacation!&nbsp; If you&#39;re vacationing with friends or other couples, this is a money saving way to vacation without sacrificing space, amenities or privacy!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plus, you can go shopping for local foods and stock your full-sized refrigerator, then make economical meals instead of eating out at restaurants every night.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '<table border="0" cellpadding