(21, 0, 'Desire Riviera Maya', 'Desire Cancun | Riviera Maya | Desire Resort Cancun', '<h1>Desire Resort Cancun, Mexico</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:2.25pt"><strong><a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/desire.asp">Desire Resort and Spa</a></strong>&nbsp;is a unique&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/couples-only-resort.asp">couples-only resort</a>, offering a world of pleasure amidst the beautiful Mexican scenery. The first and only of its kind in Mexico, Desire Resort provides an indulgent getaway for those searching for an extraordinary vacation. Desire Cancun is located on&nbsp;the city&#39;s Riviera Maya and will surround you with amazing landscape and a deliciously erotic atmosphere in which to unleash your imagination and stimulate your senses.&nbsp;<strong>Desire Resort Mexico</strong>&nbsp;is a place of unparalleled freedom, where fantasies become real and inhibitions dissolve to reveal the true cravings within all of us. You will be sharing this paradise with like-minded couples who also seek a sensuous, upscale,&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/clothing-optional.asp">clothing- optional</a>&nbsp;venue for an adventurous lifestyle experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:2.25pt"><a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/desire.asp">Desire Cancun</a>features an&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/whats_included.asp">all-inclusive</a>&nbsp;formula offering extraordinary amenities such as gourmet dining and enjoyable daily activities.&nbsp;<strong>Desire Resorts</strong>&nbsp;also provide entertainment programs for adults that will captivate and entice your sensuality like nothing you&#39;ve ever experienced. Let the&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/clothing-optional.asp">clothing-optional</a>&nbsp;concept of&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/">Desire</a>&nbsp;Resort and Spa<strong>&nbsp;</strong>seduce you while you socialize with people who share your passion for such a perfect vacation in the sun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:2.25pt">Designed as a beautiful villa, our&nbsp;adults-only resort&nbsp;offers stylish rooms and suites that blend seamlessly with the vibrant tropical atmosphere. Desire Cancun gives you breathtaking views of the gardens or majestic views of the enchanting&nbsp;Caribbean Sea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:2.25pt">With beds on soft sandy beaches,&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/">Desire</a><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Resort has all the elements required for a day of ultimate pleasure in the sun. Moments of intense relaxation await you during a luxurious treatment with your partner in our&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/spa.asp">spa</a>. No matter how you choose to enjoy your stay at&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/desire.asp">Desire Resort</a>&nbsp;</strong>&amp;&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/spa.asp">Spa</a>, our&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/clothing-optional.asp">clothing-optional</a><strong>&nbsp;</strong>hotel will create the perfect adult scenario for your forbidden fantasies to be fulfilled. Open your mind, fall under the spell, and feel...&nbsp;<a href="http://desire.originalresorts.com/">Desire</a>.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong><u>AMENITIES</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><strong>Il Piacere</strong></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">At Il Piacere, enjoy the most fascinating specialties from every corner of the world and experience the real flavors of paradise. Waiters will always be at your disposition for any special crave you may have.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">The soft lighting will transport you to far lands and submerge you in romance, intensifying your sensual culinary experience. Experience the romantic ambience of our lounge bar where you can try our high quality liquors (extra charge). The wine cava for your delight displays a selected variety of the most exclusive wine sorts there are around the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Il Piacere is open from 6:00 p.m. until 10:00 p.m. Although Desire is a clothing optional resort, this restaurant has a casual-elegant dress code. No reservations required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Haute cuisine dedicated to International specialties served in a trendy, minimalist-chic setting, chefs tasting menu available (extra $) Soft music and lighting will submerge you in romance, heightening a sensual culinary experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Dinner: 6:00 pm - 10:00 pm.</p>\r\n<span style="color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Dress code: Elegant - shirts, pants and shoes / cocktail dresses.</span>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; text-align:justify; vertical-align:middle; width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle"><img alt="Il Piacere" src="http://desire.originalresorts.com/img/Restaurants%20y%20Bars/thum_il_piacere.jpg" style="border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; height:200px; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><br />\r\n<u><strong>El Arrecife</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nEl Arrecife is an exciting restaurant of a contemporary d&eacute;cor where seductive music is played, varying with the different, special theme nights. El Arrecife is open everyday offering sumptuous breakfast buffets from 7:00 am until 11:00 am. And themed buffet dinners are held from 6:30 pm until 10:00 pm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">OUR DINNER THEME NIGHTS:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>MONDAY</strong>: Steak Night. Try our prime meat cuts such as Rib Eye, New York steaks, Tenderloin, Flank Steak, Pork Chops and Chicken prepared in any specific way you like.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>TUESDAY</strong>: Mexican Fiesta. Enjoy the real and traditional Mexican specialties that have made our gastronomy so famous around the world while the fun atmosphere turns your dinner into an unbelievable fiesta at Desire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>WEDNESDAY</strong>: Gala. Dress your best for this culinary feast. A sophisticated array of our chef&rsquo;s finest dishes will delight your senses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>THURSDAY</strong>: International. Mediterranean specialties: the perfect fusion among Spanish, French, Italian and Lebanese gourmet specialties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>FRIDAY</strong>: Brazilian Buffet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>SATURDAY</strong>: Italian Buffet. A deep appreciation for the Italian cuisine has inspired our chef to create an array of true delights that will make dinner a superb experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>SUNDAY</strong>: Tropical Delights. Begin the night, enjoying our exotic Daiquiris like blueberry and mango. Our succulent seafood specialties will be the perfect reminders you are in the Caribbean!.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Dress code: Casual. Reservations not required.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; text-align:justify; vertical-align:middle; width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle"><img alt="El Arrecife" src="http://desire.originalresorts.com/img/Restaurants%20y%20Bars/thum_arrecife.jpg" style="border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; height:200px; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Tentazione</strong></u>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Enjoy a full lunch menu including salads, ceviches and top notch main dishes with the quality, portions and presentation reminiscent of Desire&rsquo;s three specialty restaurants. This casual, central location near the main pool is ideal for those wanting to see and be seen. Also open for dinner on selected nights.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Lunch and snacks: 11:00 am &ndash; 6:00 pm<br />\r\n* The operation days will vary according to the weather conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">This restaurant is an excellent option for those who don&rsquo;t want to miss anything or anybody on the pool or the beach while having an exuberant lunch, or just a simple snack. It offers a perfect place to enjoy the best of what Desire resort has to offer: an exciting pool, an incredibly beautiful beach, beverages, top class food, and hot bodies under the golden and shinny Caribbean sun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">After having a snack, you can have a drink at the Tentazione&rsquo;s bar, which is just besides the restaurant. Tentazione is open everyday from 11:00 a.m. until 6:00 p.m. for your delight. Room service is available during operating hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">*Room service available. The operation days will vary according to the weather conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; text-align:justify; vertical-align:middle; width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle"><img alt="Tentezione" src="http://desire.originalresorts.com/img/Restaurants%20y%20Bars/thum_tentazione_restaurant.jpg" style="border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; height:200px; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><u><strong>Suki</strong></u><br />\r\nSuki is a luxurious journey into the Asian tastes and fashion. Inviting shades of red, white and dark chocolate contrast with the padded wall that offers white lights while an original ceiling, shaped as a wave, adds to the sophisticated d&eacute;cor providing the perfect setting for a stylish dinner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Suki restaurant also serves you high quality wine and of course, the traditional liquor &ldquo;Sake&rdquo; Plum Dew for an authentic Asian tour of flavor. Dinner: 6:00 pm - 10:00 pm.</p>\r\n<span style="color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Reservation required only for Tepanyaki.</span>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Enjoy the most unique dinner with a large group or in a more intimate occasion for two. You can choose either to sit on tables or in one of the two four seated sushi bars, where it is possible to admire the Tepanyaki chef do his work while he teaches you and your party small techniques, words or games of the Asian gastronomy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">This sensual dining venue of Desire Resort can only be called unique. Asian delights and daily main course specials include the freshest Sushi, tastiest Tepanyaki and most savory desserts, presented in a both intimate and mystical atmosphere.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Dress code: Elegant - shirts, pants and shoes / cocktail dresses.</span>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; text-align:justify; vertical-align:middle; width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-a