(37, 0, 'Club Ambiance Resort', 'Club Ambiance Resort | Clothing Optional Resort Jamaica | Couples Only Resort', '<strong>CLUB AMBIANCE RESORT IS AN AFFORDABLE INTIMATE &quot;IRIE VIBE&quot; TYPE CLOTHING OPTIONAL RESORT LOCATED IN RUNAWAY BAY,JAMAICA, THAT HAS A VERY AUTHENTIC TRADITIONAL JAMAICAN FEEL.&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em><strong>Club Ambiance Clothing Optional Resort</strong></em>, located in beautiful Runaway Bay Jamaica, home of the world-renowned Dunn&rsquo;s River falls. This 90 room<br />\r\nall inclusive hotel, has recently been renovated and converted into Jamaica&rsquo;s newest <strong><em>adults only clothing optional destination</em></strong>, and provides traditional style accommodations.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe location is ideal as Club Ambiance is just a short drive away from Dunn&rsquo;s River falls, an 18 hole golf course, the Martha Brae river rafting, and a quick drive to the tourist party town of Ocho Rios. <em><strong>Club Ambiance</strong></em> presents an affordable option for couples to enjoy a fantasy vacation experience, in one of the most famous tourist towns in the Caribbean. Fly into the Montego International Airport and in less than an hour you are at the resort.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe resort is beach front, and the beach is divided into three sections. One section of the beach is for those who are a little more reserved and want to keep their clothes on, the other part is clothing optional and then there is one full nude section.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nIf you are looking for an intimate setting, that offers beautiful beaches and relaxation, great food, top quality service, friendly staff all at an affordable price, you definitely have the perfect hotel in <em><strong>Club Ambiance</strong></em>. The boutique style resort is lazy during the day but provides great entertainment at night, creating the perfect balance of relaxation and party.', 'Club Ambiance provides, full bathing suit, clothing optional or <em><strong>nude sunbathing</strong></em> options to suit your needs. The swimming pool is clothing optional and very huge and the hot-tub fits about 20 to 25 people.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe resort has three bars, the pool bar, the main bar that is located in the reception area and a bar by the pier perfect for afternoon chilling and watching the sunset.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere resort has two large indoor restaurants and an outdour grill. The large indoor restaurant is also used as the stage area for the nightly shows.', '<div>There is a resident band that plays nightly and the entertainment staff also puts on nightly shows.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere are some other entertainment options in and around <em><strong>Club Ambiance</strong></em>.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div class="row-wrapper" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px;">\r\n<div class="row" style="width: auto; max-width: none; margin: 0px -15px; min-width: 0px;">\r\n<div class="six columns  b10" style="margin-bottom: 10px !important; float: left; min-height: 1px; padding: 0px 15px; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; width: 336px;"><img alt="Dunn''s Falls" src="http://clubambianceresort.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/dunns-falls-a-wow-factor.jpg" style="border:0px; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:306px" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="six columns  b10" style="margin-bottom: 10px !important; float: left; min-height: 1px; padding: 0px 15px; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; width: 336px;"><img alt="Sam, Raft Captain on Martha" src="http://clubambianceresort.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/sam-raft-captain-on-martha.jpg" style="border:0px; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:306px" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear" style="clear: both; height: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>OUTDOORS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Beaches</strong>&nbsp;with thatched sunshades, lounges, hammocks on the beach and grounds, and beaches for nude and clothing optional bathing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Swimming Pool</strong>&nbsp;with Sun Umbrellas and a Pool Bar (bar open weather and occupancy permitting).<br />\r\nBeach towels are provided at no charge</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jacuzzi</strong>, open until 01:00 am<br />\r\nBeach &amp; Pool Volleyball, Shuffleboard, Paddle Tennis, Darts, Outdoor Pool-Table, Outdoor Chess, Aerobics, Pool exercise.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>MASSAGE BEACH HUT</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Club Ambiance Unique Spa &amp; Salon offers the best in Professional Facial, Reflexology, Body Scrub, Swedish Massages, Body Wrap, Deep Tissue Massage, Relief of Bad Circulation Arthritis, Sore and Painful Muscles. Take a Relaxing moment and enjoy your healing beauty, Aroma-therapeutic Total Body Care. We assure our treatment will leave your body stress free.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="row-wrapper" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px;">\r\n<div class="row" style="width: auto; max-width: none; margin: 0px -15px; min-width: 0px;">\r\n<div class="six columns  b10" style="margin-bottom: 10px !important; float: left; min-height: 1px; padding: 0px 15px; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; width: 336px;"><img alt="Water Sports" src="http://clubambianceresort.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Water-sports.jpg" style="border:0px; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:306px" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="six columns  b10" style="margin-bottom: 10px !important; float: left; min-height: 1px; padding: 0px 15px; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; width: 336px;"><img alt="Jamaican Sunset" src="http://clubambianceresort.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/jamaican-sunset.jpg" style="border:0px; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle; width:306px" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear" style="clear: both; height: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>WATER SPORTS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>No Charge:</strong><br />\r\nPedalo&rsquo;s, Kayaks, Snorkeling Equipment for designated swimming areas only. (Snorkeling on the glass bottom boat or to other sites US$30.00 per person).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tour Desk</strong><br />\r\nThere is Tour Desk in the Lobby to book your choice of nearby attractions.<br />\r\nGolf and Deep Sea Fishing at an additional cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Diving</strong><br />\r\nWe have dive arrangements at the Tour Desk &ndash; Located in the Lobby.<br />\r\nTel. Tel. 1.876.973.6167 Ext 812.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>EVENING</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Outdoor entertainment under the stars<br />\r\nSocialize at our unique pier bar.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>INDOORS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Entertainment room with bar, pool table, reading.<br />\r\nAnd late night, enjoy dancing and socializing at our Fantasia Nightclub &amp; Disco</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'img_09850.jpg', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Club-Ambiance-Resort', 'Club Ambiance Resort is a couples only clothing optional resort located near Dunns River Falls in Runaway Bay Jamaica.', 'Club Ambiance, Club Ambiance Resort, Clothing Optional Resort Jamaica', '2013-11-28 11:55:56', 1, 15, 110, 'Clothing Optional Couples only resort conveniently located near the world famous Dunns River Falls, in Runaway Bay Jamaica. This resort has a very unique and authentic Jamaican feel, a refreshing change from the typical everyday resorts. Great for relaxation during the day and very lively at night.', 'Club Ambiance Resort', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(45, 0, 'Secrets Wild Orchid', 'Secrets Wild Orchid || Secrets Resort || Secrets Jamaica ', 'The sprawling <em><strong>Secrets Wild Orchid</strong></em> is one of the most luxurious adults-only all-inclusive resorts in Montego Bay Jamaica, just 10 minutes away from the Montego Bay Airport. At Secrets, you enjoy a wide range of all-inclusive amenities such as: a theater, a spa, a water sports and dive center, a shopping center, and a casino. These amenities are shared with the neighboring sister property Secrets St. James.<br />\r\nSome of the amenities and freebies are however reserved for the VIP guests staying in the &ldquo;Premiere&rdquo; part of the resort.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWith eight restaurants, five bars, a <em><strong>Casino</strong></em>, shops, theater and a massive spa onsite, guest staying at Secrets Wild Orchid never leave the resort. However, if you so desire, the main town of Montego Bay is only 10 minutes away on a local taxi, where the shopping and nightlife is absolutely incredible.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>What&#39;s In Your Room!!</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe rooms at <em><strong>Secrets Wild Orchid</strong></em> have sophisticated contemporary decor, and extras such as four-poster beds, MP3 docks, flat-screen TVs, soaking tubs, massive rainfall showerheads, and stocked minibars. The Premiere Swim-up Room has direct private access to the Premiere pool, as well as a whirlpool tub on the balcony, and Suites feature massive Jacuzzis in both the bathroom and on the balcony. Even the least expensive rooms, however, are attractive and high-end<br />\r\nCouples may appreciate the &ldquo;Secrets box&quot; in each room, which is essentially a non-moving dumbwaiter that allows guests to order room service without actually having to open the door for delivery. Rather, the meal is placed in the box and left for guests to access via a second door in their room.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOther in room feature includes:&nbsp;<br />\r\n37-inch flat-screen TVs with CD/DVD players<br />\r\nMinibars refreshed daily with soft drinks, bottled water, and premium beer<br />\r\nPrivate furnished balconies<br />\r\nWi-Fi (for a cost in regular rooms; free in Premiere rooms)<br />\r\nPlush bathrobes and slippers<br />\r\nIn the bathrooms: separate showers and soaking tubs, Gilchrest &amp; Soames toiletries, and magnifying make-up mirrors<br />\r\n24-hour room service<br />\r\nAir conditioning and ceiling fans<br />\r\nAlarm clocks with MP3 docking stations<br />\r\nNightly turndown service<br />\r\n&ldquo;Do Not Disturb&rdquo; light system<br />\r\nSecrets box for incognito room service delivery<br />\r\nPremiere Swim-up Rooms feature swim-out access to the Preferred Club pool, as well as private Jacuzzis on the balconies.<br />\r\nSuites have a separate bedroom, massive living room with dining table, a luxury bathroom with two-person Jacuzzi tub and rainfall showerhead,&nbsp;and big balcony with outdoor Jacuzzi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="line-height:1.6em">BOOK YOUR NEXT VACATION TO SECRETS WILD ORCHID!</strong></div>\r\n', '<strong>Pool</strong><br />\r\n<strong>A main pool, a Preferred Club pool, and a pool at neighboring Secrets St. James -- all with beach views</strong><br />\r\nThe main pools for both Secrets Wild Orchid and Secrets St. James are open to guests at either property (or at least, no one was stopping guests from moving between the two). Both are rather crowded, and each features its own swim-up bar and open-air restaurant.<br />\r\nHowever, the Preferred Club pool, which features swim-up guestrooms, an interweaving river-like design, and super-close proximity to the beach, is off-limits to non-VIP guests. Placards stating that guests must prove their Preferred Club status (via their labeled room card key) upon entering this fancier pool area are scattered around the perimeter, ensuring everyone knows their place. Of course, I walked back and forth between the two without getting asked for ID. Whether that was because of lax enforcement, or because the staff recognized me, is unclear.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Spa</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Expansive spa with extensive treatment menu and tons of extras</strong><br />\r\nThe Secrets Wild Orchid spa features more than 20 treatment rooms and palapas, as well as a menu of specialties that ranges from facials and mud baths to hydrotherapies and traditional massages. Perks include a juice bar, a relaxation room with hot and cold pools, a yoga garden, a hair salon, and a boutique. Locker rooms also include saunas, steam rooms, pressure showers, and Swiss showers.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Food</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Eight restaurants -- and yet a no-reservations policy means extra-long waits for a table</strong><br />\r\nIt might be hard to imagine that a resort boasting a total of eight restaurants would have a problem with crowds, but I witnessed guests hungrily waiting outside of every eatery on the restaurant promenade. The restaurants are shared with the neighboring Secrets St. James resort, which effectively doubles the number of guests trying to get a table. The restaurants do not accept reservations, so guests wishing to avoid a wait might want to eat early; I saw one smart couple dressed to the nines and heading to dinner at six o&rsquo;clock.<br />\r\nThe food itself, however, is impressive for an all-inclusive. There are Mexican, Italian, Jamaican, Asian-fusion, and French a la carte restaurants, as well as the obligatory buffet restaurant. Unlike a lot of other all-inclusive resorts, the atmosphere doesn&rsquo;t feel like a strip mall; each restaurant is housed in its own freestanding structure and has distinct decor.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Drinks</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Even top-shelf drinks are free, but the bars get packed</strong><br />\r\nSecrets Wild Orchid has five bars, including the main pool&rsquo;s swim-up bar, a piano bar, a music lounge, and a lobby bar. Drinks are covered in the all-inclusive rates, and that goes for the top-shelf stuff as well as the cheap rum punch and Red Stripes. Crowds jockeying for the bartenders&#39; attention start to form in the late afternoon, and it only gets worse as the evening wears on. The Secrets Wild Orchid shares its bars with neighboring Secrets St. James, and guests often take to ordering two (or three) drinks at a time to ensure they don&rsquo;t get too low while waiting for their next opportunity to order another round.<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Top-shelf liquor included in the all-inclusive rates<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Welcome cocktail and cool towel at check-in<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Weekly management cocktail parties<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Physical Activities</strong><br />\r\n<strong>A fitness center and plenty of water- and land-based sports</strong><br />\r\nSecrets Wild Orchid shares its fitness center and tennis courts with Secrets St. James. While the fitness center -- which includes cardio equipment, dumbbells, free weights, and cables -- certainly doesn&rsquo;t seem to be large enough for both resorts, which have a combined 700 rooms, it was actually quite empty both times I visited.<br />\r\nOther activities are abundant, including free tennis non-motorized water sports, dance classes, chess, darts, board games, croquet, billiards, yoga, aerobics classes, cooking classes, Ping-Pong, and jogging trails. There are also activities that come at an additional cost, such as scuba diving (first pool lesson is free), horseback riding, deep-sea fishing excursions, and golfing at a nearby championship course.<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Free non-motorized water sports, and motorized sports for a fee<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Croquet, darts, billiards, and board games<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Aerobic classes and cooking classes<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Private tennis lessons<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Business and Conventions</strong><br />\r\n<strong>More than 17,000 square feet of meeting, event, and ballroom space</strong><br />\r\nSecrets Wild Orchid provides on-site planners that can coordinate events and meetings both large and small. There are nearly a dozen different spaces that can be used for cocktail receptions, banquets, performances, business retreats, or classes. Packages are available, and guests can also create custom events.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Weddings</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Several on-site pavilions and a host of indoor venues for island nuptials</strong><br />\r\nWeddings are big business in Jamaica, and Secrets Wild Orchid is definitely in on the game, providing an exhaustive list of services ranging from on-site wedding coordinators to pressing and steaming the bride and groom&rsquo;s gown and tux. Three packages are offered, and made-to-order weddings can also be arranged. Prices for packages start around $1,000 for up to 10 guests, and all packages include a wedding cake, sparking wine, a bouquet and boutonni&egrave;re, an officiant, and free nights that go toward a future anniversary stay.<br />\r\nWhile ceremonies generally take place in one of several wedding pavilions along the beach, a vast array of meeting rooms and ballrooms are available for cocktail hours, receptions, and rehearsal dinners.<br />\r\nSecrets&rsquo; website also features a registry option in which marrying couples can request gifts be given in the form of credits toward a honeymoon at the resort.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<strong>ACTIVITIES &amp; ENTERTAINMENT</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nFrom the moment you wake in your sun-soaked suite, your days and nights are filled with nearly endless opportunities. Tennis anyone? Perhaps sailing or partying beneath the warm glow of a Caribbean moon. The choices are all yours.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Eat, drink and socialize day and night on the Promenade<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Soak in the sun poolside or on our private sugar sand beach<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Work out in our state-of-the-art fitness center<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Take to the sea for windsurfing, kayaking or snorkeling<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tee off on some of the Caribbean&rsquo;s most challenging championship golf courses*<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dance to live music or take in a show in our open-air theatre<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Large swimming pool (partially heated)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Private swimming pool for Preferred Club guests (partially heated)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2,400 feet of sugar-white beach<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Outdoor Jacuzzis<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; State-of-the-art theatre with nightly entertainment and bar service<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Open air game and entertainment palapa<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Games including ping pong, darts, pool tables, foosball, air hockey, board games, chess<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Gaming lounge with poker, keno and other gaming machines*<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sports including basketball, pool volleyball, beach football, bocce ball, soccer, water polo, lawn croquet, archery<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Batting cage<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jogging trail<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Euro bungee<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bicycle tours<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tennis court (lit) and multipurpose court<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yoga<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Aerobics and water aerobics<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Non-motorized water sports<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sailboats and kayaks<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Catamarans*<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dance classes<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cooking classes<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Windsurfing and snorkeling<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Introductory scuba lesson in the swimming pool<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Scuba diving lessons*<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Five championship golf courses (just a few minutes away)*<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Horseback riding*<br />\r\nNote: Special professional performer shows may change throughout the year. Entertainment programs could change without notice.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 'sewmb.10pv08gk-is-2430.jpg', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'secrets-wild-orchid', 'Secrets Wild Orchid is one of the most luxurious hotels in Jamaica. Conveniently located just ten minutes away from the Montego Bay Jamaca airport. Enjoy all-inclusive amenities such as, theatre, casino and more. Check out Secrets Wild Orchid.', 'Secrets wild orchid, Secrets Jamaica Secrets Resorts', '2014-04-01 18:40:21', 1, 13, 110, 'Secrets Wild Orchid is one of the most luxurious hotels in Jamaica. Conveniently located just ten minutes away from the Montego Bay Jamaca airport. Enjoy all-inclusive amenities such as, theatre, casino and more. Check out Secrets Wild Orchid.', 'Secrets Wild Orchid', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(38, 0, 'N Resort', 'Nudist Resort Jamaica | N Resort | naturist resort', 'N Resort is a beautiful all-inclusive naturist resort located in on <strong><em>Oyster Bay</em></strong>, in Falmouth Jamaica. This 96 room secluded naturist resort is located on 1000 feet of powdery white sand beach, overlooking the beautiful turquoise blue Caribbean see, just 30 minutes away from the Montego Bay International Airport. The lovely 4 star all-inclusive <em><strong>Au Natural retreat</strong></em> is exclusively for adult&rsquo;s only, couples and females. The 96 wooden rooms are spread over 12 blocks, surrounded by beautiful tropical gardens with very tasteful and tropical decor. <em><strong>N Resort </strong></em>is a very classy, rustic, laid back resort, perfect for relaxation. The staff at N will pamper you to the point that you never want to leave.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<em><strong>N Resort</strong></em> provides everything you need in for your all-inclusive vacationing, from unlimited premium liquor to gourmet dining. Find freedom and sophistication on Jamaica&#39;s North Coast at the Superb N Resort.<br />\n&nbsp;', '<h2>Dining</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/dining-room.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:224px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:274px" />Our Main Dining area at Jamaica&#39;s newest nude resort, &nbsp;is an endless smorgasbord of tropical fruits, breads, delectable pastries, freshly grilled meats and local fare. Great lunchtime trivia games and tremendous local entertainment every night to complement the supper club atmosphere at dinner time &ndash; open for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Food is available 18 hours per day.</p>\r\n<img alt="food2" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/food2.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; font-family:arial; font-size:15px; height:131px; line-height:normal; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:197px" />\r\n<p><strong>The Sabbia Italian Restaurant</strong>&nbsp;is a delightful 50 seat Restaurant &ndash; open every night for dinner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cover ups are not required in the Main Restaurant and the Italian Restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/sabbia.jpg" style="border:0px; float:right; height:131px; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; padding:0px; width:197px" />The Beach Grill - You won&#39;t have to walk too far to the most popular meeting place right on the beach! There is a Panini Grill and local specialties such as Jerk Chicken and Pork are alternated every day. A great place to graze in the nude. Naturism at it&#39;s very best :)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="spaghetti" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/spaghetti.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:169px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:190px" /><strong>The Beach Grill</strong>&nbsp;serves up some of the best jerk chicken, jerk pork and spicy Jamaican patties found anywhere on the island. &nbsp;Not to worry, favorites such as hamburgers, hot dogs, sandwiches and french fries are available too.&nbsp;Open from 11:00 am until midnight, with a full array of sandwiches, guests enjoy our all day snacks while lingering over a cold Red Stripe Beer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Sea Grape Spa</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/spa.jpg" style="border:0px; float:right; height:191px; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; padding:0px; width:128px" />The spa is located literally out on the water on a thin finger of land surrounded by the calming Caribbean sea!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At The Sea Grape Spa, while enjoying the peaceful sounds of waves lapping at our shores, guests are able to experience a myriad of distinctive spa treatments which include ancient Asian and European techniques, infused with natural Jamaican spices, fruits and minerals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/enojoy%20the%20spa.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:271px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:204px" />Here you&rsquo;ll indulge your senses with luxurious treatments from soothing facials to rejuvenating body scrubs to relaxing massages. Our professional team pampers you with calming hands, restoring your entire being back to its natural balance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your exotic spa treatment by the Caribbean Sea will surely invigorate you and be a most memorable and truly once in a lifetime experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Choose from one of our many Spa Packages listed below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ldquo;One Love&rdquo; for Two</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Experience sheer delight as two therapists synchronizes their movements to pamper both people with an indulgent massage. 55 minutes for couples</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ldquo;One Love&rdquo; at Sunset</strong>- A truly romantic and memorable massages experience for couples. Relax to the sounds of the ocean and the tranquility of dusk. 55 minutes for couples</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BODY AND BATH</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Combine one of our baths with a luxurious scrub and massage. All scrubs followed by a 20 minute massage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Select one of these invigorating scrubs. 50 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Polenta &amp; Coconut Oil Scrub<br />\r\nOrange &amp; Brown Sugar Scrub<br />\r\nPapaya &amp; Brown Sugar Scrub<br />\r\nBlue Mountain Coffee Scrub<br />\r\nSea Salt Scrub</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/drinking%20at%20the%20spa.jpg" style="border:0px; float:right; height:240px; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; padding:0px; width:362px" /><strong>Body Wraps</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Revitalizing Seaweed Wrap</strong>- a quick way to re-mineralize the body and replenish it with nutrients and elements lost on a daily basis. 50 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aloe Vera Wrap</strong>-sooth the skin after spending days in the salt and sun. The Aloe will leave your skin with healthy vibrant glow. 50 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NAIL TECHNIQUES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sea Grape Manicure<br />\r\nFrench Manicure<br />\r\nPolish Change<br />\r\nTips-Acrylics<br />\r\nNail Repair-per nail</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="spa-massage" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/spa-massage.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:227px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:341px" /><strong>SEA GRAPE SPECIAL PACKAGES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tropical Rejuvenation</strong><br />\r\n55 minute massage<br />\r\n25 minute facial<br />\r\nManicure and Pedicure Package<br />\r\nOcean Peace for You<br />\r\nThis is an ideal time to<br />\r\nRelax by the ocean, and<br />\r\nRecognize the healing power<br />\r\nIn nature.<br />\r\n55 minute massage<br />\r\n25 minute facial<br />\r\n50 minute</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Scrub<br />\r\nManicure and Pedicure<br />\r\nPackage</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Caribbean Escape</strong><br />\r\n55 minute massage<br />\r\n25 minute facial<br />\r\nPackage</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n', '<h2>Entertainment</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="entertainment-fire-man" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/entertainment-fire-man.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:244px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:308px" />At N-Resort all-inclusive hotel, Jamaica&#39;s newest nude beach resort, talented cabaret singers will entertain you, or you can show off your talent in our Staff and Guest talent show. Bedtime ends up taking a backseat to a fascinating variety of singers, dance troupes, acrobats, limbo, fire-eaters and contortionists.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also Included:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="jolly-boys-jamaica" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/jolly-boys-jamaica.jpg" style="border:0px; float:right; height:245px; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; padding:0px; width:329px" />- Floor shows featuring resident band</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Live entertainment by local Cabaret artistes and dance troupes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Disco</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Sing-a-longs at Karaoke or with the resident piano player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Staff and Guest Talent Shows</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Nakation fun for everyone!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Activites</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/young-adults-activites.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:211px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:319px" />We make sure you have the leisurely nakation you need at Jamaica&#39;s newest nudist resort, whether it&#39;s strolling nude down the mile of white sand beach next door, fine dining, tennis, excursions, frosty bar drinks, poolside games, volleyball in the pool, reading in a cabana or just lazing in a hammock to the calming sound of the waves - if it&#39;s nude recreation: you&#39;ll find it at N Resort. It&#39;s NAKATION TIME!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="nude_kayak_small" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/nude_kayak_small.jpg" style="border:0px; float:right; height:220px; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; padding:0px; width:289px" />The games room is equipped with pool tables and table tennis. We also offer day tennis. Then there is beach/pool volleyball, basketball, soccer, and cycling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our 100 ft waterslide is a fun thing &ndash; it lands you into our large swimming pool with our swim-up bar &ndash; snack bar &ndash; and conversation pool at the shallow end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Pool and nude beach volleyball</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Kayaking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Darts</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Dominoes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Board games &ndash; backgammon, monopoly, scrabble, chess, and more</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Bicycles / Cycling Trips</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Aquacise classes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Aerobic sessions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Dance classes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tennis &ndash; day only</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Table Tennis (ping pong)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Billiards (pool)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Gym and Fitness Centre &ndash; cardiovascular and weights &amp; fitness</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Basketball</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="ladies topless" src="http://n-holidays.com/images/stories/ladies%20topless.jpg" style="border:0px; float:left; height:155px; margin:0px 10px 0px 0px; padding:0px; width:234px" />Optional Tours:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Scuba Diving is available on property. S.C.U.B.A. Jamaica is P.A.D.I. Certified and offers the best in dive experiences ranging from Recreational to Professional experiences for beginners to professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Glow in the nude tours to Glistening Waters &ndash; 5 mins away &ndash; on some evenings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'n-resort-generic0.jpg', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'N-Resort-Jamaica ', 'N Resort is the Nudist Resort of Jamaica & very classy, rustic, laid back resort, perfect for relaxation. Naturist resort located in on Oyster Bay, in Jamaica.', 'N Resort, Naturist Resort Jamaica, Nudist Resort Jamaica, Au Natural Retreat', '2013-12-04 15:59:00', 1, 12, 110, 'N Resort is a beautiful all-inclusive naturist resort located in on Oyster Bay, in Falmouth Jamaica. This 96 room secluded naturist resort is located on 1000 feet of powdery white sand beach, overlooking the beautiful turquoise blue Caribbean see, just 30 minutes away from the Montego Bay International Airport.', 'N Resort', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0);
