(39, 0, 'Couples Tower Isle', 'Couple Towerl Isle | Couples Ocho Rios | Couples Resort', '<em><strong>Couples resorts</strong></em> has been one of the leading resort families in the Caribbean for over thirty five years, and <em><strong>Couples Tower Isle</strong></em>, also known as couples Ocho Rios, has been one of the cornerstones of the couples brand. The 226 rooms tropical resort has recently been decorated and its new look provides a very breezy South Beach feel. The chic contemporary d&eacute;cor features, vivid murals and ceramic by renowned artist, intricate pearlescent tile work and graphic black and white photography.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nCouples Tower Isle sits on several acres of flourishing tropical seascape. This super-all inclusive adults only, <em><strong>couples resort</strong></em>, has five lovely restaurants that provides a variety of fine dining experiences, a private island that is au natural for those who want to be naked on vacation, four bars that serves unlimited premium liquor, and a large number of excursions for you to choose from.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nTravellers choose<em><strong> Couples Tower Isle</strong></em> for a variety of reason. One of the main reasons is that, of all the Couples Resort, Couples Tower Isle offers the most reasonable prices for those looking for true value for their vacation dollars. The resort also places a huge emphasis on sporting activities such as, tennis, squash and golf. All of these, including a number of excursions are a part of your All-inclusive stay at Couples Tower Isle. Couples Tower Isle is conveniently located in the Tourist Town of Ocho Rios Jamaica, where you have easy access to great shopping, and you are a quick drive away from the world famous Dunn&rsquo;s River Falls.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<u><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>The Au Naturel Private Island</strong></span></u><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<em><strong>Couples Tower Isle</strong></em> offers a very unique experience in allowing you to have an escape within your vacation. Take a quick boat ride 100 yards away from shore, over to the man made Private Island reserved for <em><strong>Au Naturel Sunbathing</strong></em>. The island does not have a beach, but there is a private pool and bar available. There are several Cabanas available with lounge chairs, as well as lounge chairs in the sun. The Island also has palm trees and other foliage, providing adequate shade for when you want to take a break from sunbathing. Bathroom facilities present on the island, the bars are fully stocked and they bring lunch over so you can stay there all day and relax. The island is open form 9 &ndash; 5pm.', '<strong>Enjoy a refreshing dip in one of the three swimming pools, or a leisurely soak in the Jacuzzis scattered about the resort. Indulge in au naturel sunbathing on the private island, Tower Isle. Take in a game of tennis, a round of golf or while away the afternoon on a lounge chair by the sea.</strong>\r\n<ul style="margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">\r\n	<li>Three fresh water swimming pools + Jacuzzis</li>\r\n	<li>Six unique restaurants serving the finest international cuisine with Caribbean flavors: Bayside Asian, Verandah continental cuisine, Patio Mediterranean and Italian fare, Eight Rivers Caribbean fusion, Beach Grill, Veggie Caf&eacute;</li>\r\n	<li>Four bars, including the Tower Isle bar, and Piano bar, all serving premium brand liquors, wines and champagne</li>\r\n	<li>Private island for au naturel sunbathing</li>\r\n	<li>Watersports &amp; scuba</li>\r\n	<li>Synthetic grass tennis courts with lights, complimentary lesson</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited golf (transfers and green fees included. Caddy mandatory at a nominal charge)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-conditioned fitness center, with state-of the art cardio equipment.</li>\r\n	<li>Classes include spinning, aerobics, yoga, Pilates and&nbsp;more provided by certified professionals from&nbsp;<em>Fit Bodies, Inc.</em></li>\r\n	<li>Catamaran Cruises</li>\r\n	<li>Glass-bottom boat tour</li>\r\n	<li>Dunn&#39;s River Falls tour</li>\r\n	<li>Shopping excursion to Downtown Ocho Rios</li>\r\n	<li>Shuttle to Island Village, home of Jimmy Buffett&#39;s &quot;Margaritaville&quot;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h1>A host of delightful dining options awaits at Couples Tower Isle.&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<strong>From gourmet indoor dinners at Eight Rivers&mdash;evoking the days of old Jamaica&mdash;to delightful al fresco meals at the perennially chic Verandah, guests are sure to find the perfect meal to tempt their taste buds.</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Under the auspices of Executive Chef Stephan Spath, every menu has been thoughtfully crafted using only the finest local produce, seafood and spices&mdash;to deliver a dining experience as delicious as it is authentic.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="top-margin-n" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(100, 100, 105); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; margin-top: 22px !important;">\r\n<h2>PATIO RESTAURANT&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(BREAKFAST/LUNCH/DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Breakfast features and array of fresh fruits, freshly baked breads and pastries, and made to serve omelets. For lunch and dinner, enjoy Italian and Mediterranean cuisine.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Continental Breakfast: 5:30am<br />\r\nFull Breakfast: 7:30am to 10:30am<br />\r\nLunch: 12:30pm to 2:30pm<br />\r\nDinner: 6:30pm to 10:00pm, closed&nbsp;Sundays,&nbsp;Mondays&nbsp;and&nbsp;Wednesdays&nbsp;<br />\r\nReservations: Not Required<br />\r\nDress: Resort Casual (beach cover up, footwear required)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>THE VERANDAH&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Enjoy continental fare in a Caribbean chic space, overlooking the Caribbean Sea and Tower Isle.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Dinner: 6:30pm to 10:30pm, closed Mondays, Thursdays&nbsp;and Saturdays&nbsp;<br />\r\nReservations: Not Required<br />\r\nDress: Resort Chic<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>BAYSIDE&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Feast on Asian spring rolls, Pad Thai and banana leaf-steamed snapper by candlelight, overlooking the Caribbean Sea.</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Dinner: 6:00pm to 9:00pm, closed&nbsp;Mondays and&nbsp;Saturdays&nbsp;<br />\r\nReservations: Required<br />\r\nDress: Resort Chic</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>EIGHT RIVERS&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Experience Jamaica of old, and enjoy divine gourmet dining featuring continental cuisine with a distinctly Caribbean flair.</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Dinner: 6:15pm to 9:00pm, closed Mondays<br />\r\nReservations: Required<br />\r\nDress: Cocktail Elegant (Jeans, sneakers, flip flops and shorts are not permitted)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>POOL GRILL&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(ALL DAY/NIGHT)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>To satisfy your cravings any time of the day or night, the Pool Grill offers a variety of mouthwatering sandwiches, salads, jerk chicken, and Jamaican patties.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Daily: 11:00am to 6:00pm and 10:30pm to 5:00am<br />\r\nNo dress code, swimwear acceptable</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>VEGGIE BAR&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(LUNCH/ALL DAY)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Delight with our fresh juice of the day, fruit smoothies, veggie dips and delectable healthy salads and sandwiches.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Daily: 11:00am to 6:00pm<br />\r\nNo dress code, swimwear acceptable<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>IN SUITE DINING</h2>\r\n<strong>Daily 7:30am to 9:30pm</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>PRIVATE DINING ON THE BEACH</h2>\r\n<strong>For the ultimate in romantic evenings, allow our talented culinary team to create an unforgettable private candle-lit meal for you under the stars&mdash;complete with Couples private label wine, three delectable courses of Caribbean&mdash;inspired cuisine and the soothing sounds of the waves lapping onto the beach.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>To reserve your private dinner, please contact the&nbsp;<a href="http://support.couples.com/index.php?_mo=st&amp;department=11" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">Romance Concierge</a>&nbsp;in advance or visit the guest services desk upon arrival. The dinner is $170 per couple. If you prefer a more exclusive experience, ask about our Tower Isle Dinner. For only $240 you will be ferried offshore to legendary Tower Isle for a remarkable dinner with a romantic view of your resort from the island.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>SPECIAL NIGHTS AT COUPLES TOWER ISLE</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday Night Beach Party Barbeque: Enjoy delectable grills and Caribbean specialties on the beach.</li>\r\n	<li>Monday Repeat Guest Dinner: An&nbsp;Invitation&nbsp;will be delivered to your room.</li>\r\n	<li>Friday Lobster Night: All Restaurants serve lobster specialties, in season July 1 to March 31</li>\r\n	<li>Saturday Night: A celebration of gourmet cuisine from around the world.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h1>Honored as&nbsp;<em>Travel+Leisure&rsquo;s</em>&nbsp;&ldquo;Best Caribbean Spa&rdquo;&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<strong>the Oasis Spa at Couples Tower Isle is a haven of tranquility. Designed from a Zen point of view, the pure white treatments rooms cluster around an outdoor Buddha plunge pool. Deep cushion lounge chairs frame the perimeter of the pool&mdash;an open invitation to spend some time soaking in the calm or sipping a fresh drink from the juice bar, before or after your treatment.</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite you to peruse our extensive list of spa services&mdash;including our celebrated massage styles, seaweed wraps and body scrubs. Please be sure to inquire at the spa reservations desk for any specialty treatments available exclusively at Couples Tower Isle.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h2>BARS &amp; NIGHTLIFE</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy the festive atmosphere while sipping a Couples Kiss or Rum Punch&mdash;signature cocktails, designed by your Couples Tower Isle mixologist. After dinner, we invite you to sample from a world of local and international musical talent&mdash;from steel drums to soul, from reggae rhythms to rock &#39;n&#39; roll, there&#39;s a beat to match every mood. End your evening 50s&#39; Hollywood style, at our vintage Piano Bar&mdash;for great entertainment into the late night hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*&nbsp;Restaurant schedule may be subject to seasonal adjustments</p>\r\n', 'There are a variety of daily activities available at Couple Tower Isles. This includes:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTennis Lessons<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSquash<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGolf<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPower Walks<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBoard Games', '121812-couples-tower-isle-aso-612x339-10.jpg', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Couples-Tower-Isle', 'Couples Tower Isle, also known as Ocho Rios. The super-all inclusive adults only, couples resort, a private island for those who want to be naked on vacation. ', 'Couples Tower Isle, Couples Ocho Rios, Couples Resort', '2013-12-05 09:02:44', 1, 15, 110, 'Couples Tower Isle, located in Ocho Rios Jamaica is a part of the Couples Resort family. This beautiful resort is very famous for it Au Naturel Private Island just 100 yards off shore. Couples Resorts is a leading resort brand in the Caribbean and Worldwide. ', 'Couples Towel Isle', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(40, 0, 'Couples Negril', 'Couples Negril | Couples Resort Negril', '<em><strong>Couples Negril</strong></em> is located at the top of the beautiful Seven Mile white sand beach in <em><strong>Negril Jamaica</strong></em>. The Resort has 234 rooms and offers an all-inclusive, couples only luxury vacation concept. <em><strong>Couples Resort</strong></em> sits on over 18 acres of land, providing a very spacious surrounding with a very tropical rainforest like feel. This creates a very romantic ambiance for couples looking for that magical getaway. &nbsp;The 3 story beachfront buildings have a very rustic finish in vibrant tropical colors. Each of the rooms provides the typical, Flat Screen TV&#39;s, CD Player, a safe, coffee maker and ironing board.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhen you stay at<em><strong> Couples Negril</strong></em>, expect to experience the finest of Jamaica&#39;s soft pearly white sand beach. The Beach is spectacular and runs the entire length of the resort, and the hotel staff does an amazing job of raking and keeping it clean daily. Your all-inclusive holiday at Couples means way more than just your typical all inclusive meals and drinks. All activities at Couples are free which includes, Tennis, Sailing, snorkeling, scuba diving, with the only exception being golf. Exceptional cuisine, midnight bonfires, moonlight dinners on the beach are some of the things you can expect at <em><strong>Couples Negri</strong></em>l.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<img alt="" src="http://couples.com/_img/negril-caribbean-spa.jpg" />\r\n<h1>Praised as the &ldquo;Best Spa in the Caribbean&rdquo; by&nbsp;<em>Travel+Leisure</em>,&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<strong>the Oasis Spa at Couples Negril fully embraces its idyllic setting by offering its exclusive treatments in organic therapy rooms, an open-air thatched hut on the beach, or in the tucked away intimacy of the Tree House.</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Indulge in a variety of massages that soothe away any lingering tension, revive with detoxifying seaweed wraps and soften even the most tired skin with moisture-rich body scrubs and poultices&mdash;all the while letting the brush of the palms lull you into a deep and abiding state of bliss.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our salon&rsquo;s stylists are also available to pamper you. Services include manicures, pedicures, hair styling, hair conditioning, and waxing and hot towel shaves for men.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://couples.com/_img/negril-couples-restaurant.jpg" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>The delightful restaurants at Couples Negril create an intimate ambiance for two,</h1>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>while also encouraging easy interaction with fellow guests&mdash;serving the finest cuisine made with fresh local produce and a variety of seafood.</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Feast on the extravagant breakfast buffets at the poolside Cassava Terrace, delight in the nuances of Asian cuisine at the refined Lychee eatery or explore the gourmet dishes of Jamaica at the acclaimed Otaheite restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="top-margin-n" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(100, 100, 105); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; margin-top: 22px !important;">\r\n<h2>CASSAVA TERRACE&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(BREAKFAST/LUNCH/DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Open air dining at its most delicious. Breakfast features an array of fresh fruits, freshly baked breads and pastries, and made to serve omelets. For lunch and dinner, our salads and fresh seafood are a must.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Continental Breakfast: 5:30am<br />\r\nFull Breakfast: 7:30am to 10:30am<br />\r\nLunch: 12:30pm to 2:30pm<br />\r\nDinner: 6:30pm to 10:00pm, closed Thursday<br />\r\nReservations: Not Required<br />\r\nDress: Resort Casual (beach cover up, footwear required)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>BEACH GRILL&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(LUNCH)</span>&nbsp;HELICONIA&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Feast on casual fare featuring grills, salads and Jamaica delights&rsquo; during the day and sample grilled specialties and Mediterranean cuisine at night, under the stars.&nbsp;</strong>view Beach Grill<strong>&nbsp;/&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;Heliconia\r\n\r\n<p>Lunch: 11:00 am to 6:00 pm (swimwear acceptable)<br />\r\nDinner: 6:30pm to 10:30pm, closed Saturdays<br />\r\nAfter Hours: 11:00pm to5:00am (Beach Grill)<br />\r\nReservations: Not Required<br />\r\nDress: Resort Casual (in the evening)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>LYCHEE&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Experience a taste of Asian served in a casual chic ambiance. With a view to the open kitchen, watch our chefs create your favorite dishes. &nbsp;</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Dinner: 6:00pm to 9:15pm, closed Mondays<br />\r\nReservations: Not required<br />\r\nDress: Elegant casual. Shirts, slacks/dress shorts and closed-toe shoes or dress sandals for the gentlemen and summer dresses for the ladies. No flip flops, T-shirts, beach shorts, jeans, sneakers, or hats are allowed. Jacket is optional.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>OTAHEITE&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(100, 100, 105)">(DINNER)</span></h2>\r\n<strong>Otaheite, named after the Jamaican apple, denotes the quintessentially authentic Caribbean dining experience in an intimate and elegant setting.&nbsp;</strong>view&nbsp;&raquo;\r\n\r\n<p>Dinner: 6:15pm to 8:45pm, closed Thursdays<br />\r\nReservations: Required<br />\r\nDress: Cocktail Elegant (no jeans; jacket optional)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PRIVATE DINING ON THE BEACH</h2>\r\n<strong>For the ultimate in romantic evenings, allow our talented culinary team to create an unforgettable private candle-lit meal for you under the stars&mdash;complete with Couples&rsquo; private label wine, three delectable courses of Caribbean-inspired cuisine and the soothing sounds of the waves lapping onto the beach.</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>To reserve your private dinner, please contact the&nbsp;<a href="http://support.couples.com/index.php?_mo=st&amp;department=11" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">Romance Concierge</a>&nbsp;in advance or visit the guest services desk upon arrival. The dinner is $170 per couple.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>IN-SUITE DINING</h2>\r\n<strong>For guests staying in Garden or Beachfront Suites special in-room dining menu is offered. Dinner can be served between 6:30pm and 9:00pm. Please order a day in advance.</strong>\r\n\r\n<h2>SPECIAL NIGHTS AT COUPLES NEGRIL</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Friday Chocolate Sunset: 6:00pm on the boardwalk</li>\r\n	<li>Friday Lobster Night: All Restaurants will serve lobster specialties, in season July 1 &ndash; March 31.</li>\r\n	<li>Monday Managers Cocktail Party: 6:30pm</li>\r\n	<li>Monday Repeat Guest Dinner Night: 7:00pm cocktails and 7:30pm dinner at Otaheite. An invitation will be delivered to your room.</li>\r\n	<li>Tuesday Wine and Cheese Cocktail Party: 6:30pm in the Piano Bar</li>\r\n	<li>Wednesday Honeymooners Reception: 6:30pm in the Piano Bar</li>\r\n	<li>Thursday Beach Party: 7:00pm on the beach, under the stars</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>BARS &amp; NIGHTLIFE</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy the festive atmosphere while sipping a Paradise Passion or Sunset Serenade&mdash;signature Couples Negril cocktails. After dinner, we invite you to sample from a world of local and international musical talent&mdash;from steel drums to soul, from reggae rhythms to rock &lsquo;n&rsquo; roll, there&rsquo;s a beat to match every mood. The piano bar offers a chic indoor setting for cocktails and live entertainment five nights of the week&mdash;and transforms itself for the remaining two into a lively nightclub that will inspire you to kick up your heels.</p>\r\n', '<h1>Located on 18 acres of the purest white sand in Jamaica, Couples Negril was designed as a beachfront playground&mdash;offering every activity imaginable.&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<strong>From scuba to sailing, snorkeling to pool volleyball, the water adventures know no bounds. For land-lovers, complimentary tennis, unlimited golf, and a pristine fitness center beckon.</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">\r\n	<li>Two swimming pools &amp; four jacuzzis</li>\r\n	<li>Five unique restaurants serving the finest international cuisine with Caribbean flavors: Cassava Terrace, Beach Grill, Otaheite Fine Dining, Heliconia Mediterranean Gourmet, Lychee Asian fusion cuisine</li>\r\n	<li>Four bars, including swim-up and piano, all serving premium brand liquors and wines</li>\r\n	<li>Private beach section for au naturel sunbathing</li>\r\n	<li>Watersports &amp; Scuba</li>\r\n	<li>Tennis courts with lights, complimentary lessons</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited golf (transfers and green fees included. Caddy mandatory at a nominal charge)</li>\r\n	<li>Fitness center with state-of the art cardio and weights.</li>\r\n	<li>Classes include spinning, aerobics, yoga, Pilates&nbsp;and more provided by certified professionals from&nbsp;<em>Fit Bodies, Inc</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Glass-bottom boat tour</li>\r\n	<li>Catamaran cruise</li>\r\n	<li>Shuttle to Margaritaville</li>\r\n	<li>Shopping excursions to downtown Negril</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'negril-sl-walk-on-the-beach0.jpg', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Couples-Negril', 'Couples Negril is located at the top of the beautiful Seven Mile white sand beach in Negril Jamaica. Offers you all-inclusive, couples only luxury vacation.', 'Couples Negril, Couples Resort, Negril Jamaica', '2013-12-06 17:08:01', 1, NULL, 110, 'Couples Negril is located at the top of the world famous Seven-Mile white sand beach in Negril Jamaica. The resort sits on nearly 18 acres of land and offers a very tropical rainforest like landscape. Couples Negril provide a small clothing optional area for those interested in a bit of nude sunbathing.', 'Couples Negril', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(41, 0, 'Club Orient', 'Club Orient | Orient Bay | Nude Beach St, Martin', '<em><strong>Club Orient</strong></em> is <em><strong>nudist family resort</strong></em> located on the beautiful and famous <em><strong>Orient Bay</strong></em> in St. Martin. Club Orient is located on the French side of the tiny island, with more than 35 beaches. The resort offers one hundred and thirty seven (137) spacious oceanfront, or garden bungalows. With all units coming fully equipped with a kitchen, dining area, air conditioning units, internet access, front and back verandas and other features, making Club Orient the perfect home away from home. The onsite amenities include, a grocery store, boutique, watersports facility, spa and fitness center, restaurants, a beach bar and grill, and tennis courts, car rentals and a business center.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<em><strong>Club Orient</strong></em> is not <em><strong>Hedonistic</strong></em> is not a lifestyle venue. Club Orient is more for the naturist looking to enjoy a relaxing, serene vacation in a beautiful, peaceful tropical setting. Club Orient is the only nudist resort on the friendly island of St. Martin, in the French West Indies, The average annual temperature is 85 degrees Fahrenheit; so expect beautiful weather regardless of what time of the year you visit. The beach is absolutely stunning. White sand, crystal clear water, a barrier reef and three uninhabited islands within makes this the perfect tropical getaway<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWhether you stay in one of the luxurious villas, or you stay in a chalet, <em><strong>Club Orient</strong></em> gives you a naturist vacation experience like you will never find anywhere else.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<p><strong>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><a class="nonblock" href="http://www.cluborient.com/la-boutique.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; -webkit-transform-origin: 0% 0%; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);"><strong>La Boutique</strong></a