(42, 0, 'Couples San Souci', 'Couples San Souci | Couples Resort | Couples Jamaica', '<em><strong>Couples San Souci, </strong></em>one of Jamaica&#39;s first all-inclusive hotels built in 1943<em><strong>,&nbsp;</strong></em>is nestled on the cliffs of Jamaica&#39;s emerald coast and sits above a stretch of the beautiful turquois Caribbean Sea. Couples San Souci, voted one of the top wedding resort is the Caribbean is located in the very hip, trendy tourist town of Ocho Rios, known for it&#39;s many attractions, such as<em><strong> Dunn&rsquo;s River falls</strong></em>, that is just 15 minutes away. Getting to couples San Souci is just about a 50-minute scenic drive from the Montego Bay International Airport.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Resort<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nCouples San Souci is a 150-room all-inclusive couples only hotel, beautifully decorated with terraces, fountains, and spectacular gardens, bordered by the very calm sea to the North. The resort has a fine Italian Restaurant, six bars, and an amazing spa that offers a natural mineral spring. With luxurious ocean front accommodations, ranging from one bedroom suites to suites over 1200 square ft., <em><strong>Couples San Souci</strong></em> is perfect for couples looking for a romantic five star holiday experience. Every suite enjoys air conditioning, a fully stocked mini-bar that is replenished daily, and state-of-the-art entertainment options such as an IPOD/MP3 player and a satellite cable flat screen LCD TV. The well-appointed bathroom features a shower or bathtub; Gilchrist &amp; Soames bath products, cozy bathrobes and a salon-style hair dryer. Additional amenities include an iron, ironing board, in-room safe, telephone and nightly turndown service.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>The resort offers a private beack area for those who wish to get naked while on vacation at Couples San Souci. This reservede beach area is mandatory nude.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet AVP&#39;s travel specialist help you book your luxury all inclusive couples only getaway to <em><strong>Couples San Souci</strong></em>. &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<h1>A host of delightful dining options awaits at Couples Sans Souci.</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>From elegant country club dining on the sweeping terrace of Casanova to casual meals in the sand at the Beach Grill, the dining options at Couples Sans Souci never fail to please.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Authentic Jamaican specialties&mdash;made with only the finest local ingredients and spices&mdash;may be enjoyed alongside a worldly menu of international favorites. At the end of the night, saunter up to the polished wooden counter of the Balloon Bar&mdash;and feel like you traveled back in time.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/palazzina-restaurant.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>PALAZZINA<span style="font-size:16px">(breakfast/lunch/dinner)</span></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>Enjoy bistro fare from around the world in an elegant indoor dining room on the terrace. Open for breakfast, lunch and dinner with table service.</p>\r\n\r\n	<div class="show-hide-links" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px;">view sample menu &raquo;&nbsp;view restaurant &raquo;&nbsp;view info &amp; hours &raquo;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="clear-fix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 1px; clear: both; width: 698px; overflow: hidden;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/beach-grill-bella-vista.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>BEACH GRILL&nbsp;<span style="font-size:16px">(lunch)</span>&nbsp;BELLA VISTA&nbsp;<span style="font-size:16px">(dinner)</span></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>For casual dining on the beach, enjoy grills and fresh salads for lunch and authentic Jamaica specialties for a delectable dinner.</p>\r\n\r\n	<div class="show-hide-links" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px;">view sample menu &raquo;&nbsp;view restaurant &raquo;&nbsp;view info &amp; hours &raquo;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="clear-fix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 1px; clear: both; width: 698px; overflow: hidden;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/casanova-restaurant.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>CASANOVA&nbsp;<span style="font-size:16px">(dinner)</span></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>In a style of understated colonial elegance, Casanova&#39;s menu features an eclectic mix of international cuisine, Caribbean ingredients for elegant dining indoors or out.</p>\r\n\r\n	<div class="show-hide-links" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px;">view sample menu &raquo;&nbsp;view restaurant &raquo;&nbsp;view info &amp; hours &raquo;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="clear-fix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 1px; clear: both; width: 698px; overflow: hidden;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/in-suite-dining.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>IN SUITE DINING</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>Daily 6:00am to 11:00pm</p>\r\n\r\n	<div class="show-hide-links" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px;">view sample menu &raquo;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="clear-fix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 1px; clear: both; width: 698px; overflow: hidden;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/private-beach-dining.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>PRIVATE DINING ON THE BEACH<span style="font-size:16px">(dinner)</span></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>For the ultimate in romantic evenings, allow our talented culinary team to create an unforgettable private candle-lit meal for you under the stars&mdash;complete with Couples private label wine, three delectable courses of Caribbean&mdash;inspired cuisine and the soothing sounds of the waves lapping onto the beach.</p>\r\n\r\n	<div class="show-hide-links" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px;">view info &amp; hours &raquo;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="clear-fix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 1px; clear: both; width: 698px; overflow: hidden;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/bars-nightlife.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>BARS &amp; NIGHTLIFE</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>Couples Sans Souci&#39;s six unique bars offer the ideal setting to enjoy your favorite drink or sample one of ours&mdash;the Sans Souci Exotic Cooler. With live nightly entertainment under the stars&mdash;from steel drums to soul, from reggae rhythms to rock &#39;n&#39; roll, there&#39;s a beat to match every mood. Our lively disco nights on Sunset Beach will inspire you to dance the night away under the stars.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="clear-fix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 1px; clear: both; width: 698px; overflow: hidden;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative; color: rgb(100, 100, 105); font-family: Ubuntu, ''Trebuchet MS'', Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/restaurants-bars/special-nights.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>SPECIAL NIGHTS AT COUPLES SANS SOUCI</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>Monday Managers Cocktail Party: 6:00pm at the main pool</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Tuesday Beach Party: 7:00pm on the main beach</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Wednesday Repeat Guest Dinner: 7:00pm at the main pool. An invitation will be delivered to your room.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Wednesday Lobster Night: every restaurant serves lobster specialties when in season, July 1 - March 31</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Friday Starlight Gala: 7:30pm on the main lawn</p>\r\n\r\n	<div class="show-hide-links" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>The Spa -&nbsp;\r\n	<h1>Imagine yourself in a private cabana at the edge of the cliffs</h1>\r\n\r\n	<p>With the sound of the ocean below, as one of our expert therapists melts away your stress with a deep tissue massage. It&#39;s delights like these that make our signature spa services so enticing&mdash;and have garnered us the honor of being named the Best Caribbean Spa by&nbsp;<em>Travel + Leisure</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Indulge in an extensive menu of relaxing massages, reviving body wraps and scrubs, reflexology, and pampering beauty treatments.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Our salon&#39;s stylists are also available to pamper you. Services include manicures, pedicures, hair styling, hair conditioning and repair, waxing and hot towel shaves for men.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1>In addition to the&nbsp;exceptional inclusions, your stay at Couples Sans Souci offers a wealth of thrilling activities.</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Dive into our pristine mineral pool and enjoy the rejuvenating benefits of natural spring water. Frolic in the waves. Explore the coral reefs. Play a round of golf. Take a professional tennis lesson. Or simply sail a boat into the sunset.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class="cc-row" style="margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 698px; clear: both; display: table; table-layout: auto; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-spot cc-column one-third" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 10px 0px 0px; border-color: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; display: table-cell; width: 222px; overflow: hidden;"><img class="inclusion-photo" src="http://couples.com/_img/sans-souci/activities/water-activities.jpg" style="border:0px solid; display:block; height:auto; margin:0px; outline:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:222px" /></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="row-meta cc-column fill" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: table-cell; width: auto !important; position: relative;">\r\n	<div class="row-meta-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 45px; border: 0px solid; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 466px; height: inherit; min-height: inherit; position: relative;">\r\n	<h2>WATER ACTIVITIES</h2>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>4 Swimm