(43, 0, 'Grand Lido Negril', 'Grand Lido | Grand Lido Negril | Grand Lido Resort', '<em><strong>Grand Lido Negril</strong></em> is located on the seven-mile beach in Negril Jamaica. The resort was owned by Superclubs for many years, operated under the name Grand Lido before it was changed to <em><strong>Breezes Grand Negril</strong></em>, and then it was recently bought by <em><strong>Blue Diamond Resorts</strong></em>, who restored the original name and concept back to Grand Lido Negril.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nGrand Lido Negril is an adult&rsquo;s only all-inclusive hotel, nestled on a 2.5 mile bay of powdery white sand, with a stunning view of the Caribbean Sea. Guest of this legendary resort enjoy, spacious junior or one bedroom suites, five amazing restaurants, exceptional spa service, and the opportunity to witness one of the most beautiful sunsets in the Caribbean. Grand Lido Negril provides a relaxed tropical atmosphere, perfect for young adults, couples and singles. The resort has 210 suites, and with both clothed and an <em><strong>Au Naturel Beach facilities</strong></em>.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nYou all inclusive stay at <em><strong>Grand Lido Negril</strong></em> includes, unlimited premium alcohol, unlimited meals, free Wi-Fi throughout the resort, unlimited phone calls from your room to North America and Europe, free introductory scuba lessons, stocked fridge in your room, nightly entertainment, concierge service, and in-room electric safes.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nBook your stay at <em><strong>Grand Lido Negril</strong></em> With AdultVacationParties.com!<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<h1>Restaurants &amp; Bars at Grand Lido Negril Resort &amp; Spa</h1>\r\n<strong>Taste the Decadence</strong><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Premium cocktails and exotic tropical creations flow from the bars located throughout the grounds, and there&#39;s always a delicious snack sizzling on our outdoor grills. Embark on a journey of gastronomic decadence at any of our 6 themed restaurants, with the freshest, most delicious ingredients, prepared by world-class chefs.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>BUFFET RESTAURANT</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Indulge in lavish, buffet-style breakfasts, lunches and dinners in the resort`s main dining room, which features warm ambiance with tropical d&eacute;cor. Start your day off with an assortment of local and international favourites, and don&#39;t miss the world famous Jamaican coffee. We feature 2 sumptuous dinner buffets each week: An extravagant Caribbean Beach Carnival Night, and a spectacular General Manager&#39;s Grand Gala.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>CONTINENTAL CUISINE</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Come and enjoy Continental cuisine served up Grand Lido-style in air conditioned comfort, featuring a selection of popular a la carte dishes with an international flavour. Dinner Dress Code: Evening casual</span>\r\n\r\n<h3><br />\r\nITALIAN RESTAURANT</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">This casual dining atmosphere serves up delicious a la carte Italian cuisine. Dine indoors in a European caf&eacute; setting with air conditioning, or outside in the warm Caribbean breeze. Dinner Dress Code: Evening casual</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>FRENCH RESTAURANT</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Enjoy a wonderful mix of aromas, textures, and flavours artistically arranged on the plate using the freshest of local ingredients to bring out the natural flavour. A la carte and air conditioned. Dinner Code: Evening casual&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>JAPANESE RESTAURANT</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">This charming Asian-style restaurant overlooks the azure Caribbean waters. Enjoy the cooking show at the teppanyaki tables, or watch our chef hand-roll delectable sushi at the sushi bar. Air conditioned. Dinner Dress code: Evening casual&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>JAMAICAN RESTAURANT</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Experience spicy, authentic Jamaican fare at its best in an inviting, island atmosphere. Our waiters and waitresses will happily take your order with true Jamaican hospitality. Learn some Patois and sample the signature drinks served exclusively at this restaurant. Dinner Dress Code: Evening casual.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>BAR SERVICE</h3>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">All of our 6 bars are stocked with premium international and local brands of liquor and wines. Call out your favourite cocktail, or have one of our master mixers pour you a signature drink.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Choose from 2 beach bars, the main bar, a piano bar, the disco bar, and an authentic Jamaican themed bar. Whether you&#39;re in the mood to sip a cocktail from your lounger, or participate in Karaoke, we have the perfect venue to enjoy your drink of choice.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Spa Services at Grand Lido Negril Resort &amp; Spa</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Feel the Relaxation</strong></p>\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Guests can enjoy a wide selection of spa services including Massages Reflexology, and Beauty treatments, Our therapeutic facilities have a Hot Jacuzzi, Cold Plunge Pool, Sauna &amp; Steam Room. Here only the finest natural ingredients from land and sea are used in all spa treatments, products and facials to maintain a balance with nature and enhance the mind, body and spirit connection.</span>', '<div class="content_wrapper" style="width: 950px; float: left; padding-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">\r\n<div class="arial12N_676767" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); line-height: 18px; padding: 20px;">\r\n<h1><span style="color:#000000">Things to do at Grand Lido Negril Resort &amp; Spa</span></h1>\r\n<span style="color:#000000"><strong>Hear the Cheering</strong><br />\r\nBeach volleyball, table tennis, trivia games, nature walks, mixology classes, cooking classes, aerobics and reggae classes are only some of the many activities in which our guests can participate. The Fitness Center is furnished with professional equipment. There are 4 tennis courts on location, 2 of which can be lit for night play at an additional cost.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur main pool is located between the main beach and the terrace, while the other is located in the tranquil west end of the hotel. There are 5 Jacuzzis located throughout the property.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><span style="color:#000000"><img alt="" src="http://grandlidoresorts.com/images/img_indoor.jpg" style="float:right; height:159px; width:173px" />INDOOR ACTIVITIES</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color:#000000">Backgammon, cards, dominos, pool tables, table tennis, and several board games are available for your enjoyment in the Games Room.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><span style="color:#000000">NIGHTLY ENTERTAINMENT</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color:#000000">After a fun-filled day, unwind and free your spirit at our Piano Bar, night club, or by catching some live nightly entertainment. Enjoy karaoke, steel drum bands, local rhythms, game shows, theme nights, and so much more.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="footer_wrapper" style="width: 918px; float: left; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 236); border: 1px solid rgb(226, 219, 153); padding: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 'grandlidonegril-80.jpg', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Grand-Lido-Negril', 'Grand Lido Negril - Spacious suites |Amazing restaurants |Spa service | including unlimited alcohol |Meal | nightly entertainment Free Wi-Fi throughout Resort.', 'Grand Lido Negril, Breezes Grand Negril, Blue Diamond Resorts', '2013-12-12 15:16:33', 1, NULL, 110, 'Grand Lido Negril is an adultÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s only all-inclusive hotel, nestled on a 2.5 mile bay of powdery white sand, with a stunning view of the Caribbean Sea. Guest of this legendary resort enjoy, spacious junior or one bedroom suites, five amazing restaurants, exceptional spa service, and the opportunity to witness one of the most beautiful sunsets in the Caribbean. Grand Lido Negril provides both clothing and Au Naturel beach facilities.', 'Grand Lido Negril', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(48, 0, 'Sunset At The Palms', 'Sunset At The Palms || Sunset Resorts', '<em><strong>Sunset at the Palms</strong></em> is an adult only all-inclusive resort located in Negril Jamaica. A part of the <em><strong>Sunset Resorts </strong></em>family, this resort features, trendy new design, sumptuously appointed guestrooms, new amenities and lush landscaping.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nEnjoy International and authentic Jamaican cuisine. The Palm Grove restaurant has open-air dining and a buffet-style breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Dress in your elegant resort-wear best and sample &agrave; la Carte specialties from the eclectic Asian-fusion menu at the Lotus Leaf. Getting hungry at the beach? The Palm Breeze Beach Bar &amp; Grill has sandwiches and Jamaican &quot;jerk&quot; favorites, with Red Stripe beer or other cool refreshments to wash them down.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nIf you are hanging out at the pool at &quot;Sunset At The Palms, swim up to the Bamboo Bar to refresh your spirits or pull up a stool after dark for a tropical drink before the night begins. Enjoy an afternoon of <strong>live music</strong> at the Martini Lobby Bar or join friends to sip a signature martini before dinner<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nDiscover 85 &ldquo;treehouse-style&rdquo; guestrooms, standing amidst a ten-acre tropical garden, praised by Architectural Digest. And it&rsquo;s all just steps from the resort&rsquo;s five-acre beachfront facilities and two miles of white, sandy beach, hailed as the most blissful beach in Jamaica. From the martini bar to the beach bar, Sunset at the Palms delivers the best of Jamaica&rsquo;s beauty and endless charm. See for yourself why TripAdvisor.com has named <em><strong>Sunset at the Palms</strong></em> one of the top ten most romantic resorts in the Caribbean.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<strong>Sunset at the Palms Resort</strong> is an intimate and chic adult&#39;s only boutique escape set in a ten-acre tropical garden. Each suite has a tree-house style design, a delightful way to immerse yourself in the &quot;capital of cool&quot; Negril.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Naturalistic luxury accommodations</li>\r\n	<li>Romantic adults only retreat</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited premium brands &amp; fine dining</li>\r\n	<li>Stay connected with complimentary Wi-Fi</li>\r\n	<li>Nature lovers... tropical paradise</li>\r\n	<li>Private beach club</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', '', 'sunsetpalms40.png', '1405978864_', '1405978864_', NULL, NULL, 'Sunset-at-the-palms', 'Sunset At The Palms resorts is a beautiful adults only resort located on the 7-mile beach in Negril Jamaica.', 'Sunset At The Palms, Sunset Resorts', '2014-07-21 14:41:05', 1, 13, 110, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
(49, 0, 'Jewel Dunns River', 'Jewel Dunns River|| Jewel Dunns River Fall|| Jewel Resort Jamaica', 'The <strong>Jewel Dunn&rsquo;s River Falls</strong> beach resort, is a premium Jamaica all-inclusive, adults-only resort just minutes from one of the main attractions of Jamaica. Located in beautiful Ocho Rios, the Jewel is the perfect place for a holiday in the tropics.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nOur all-inclusive resort offers unique Jamaican exclusive, &quot;Jewel Only&quot;, that you can only find here.<br />\r\nThere are several restaurants at the Jewel Dunn&rsquo;s River; the more formal platinum, the casual Aquamarina Beach Bar &amp; Grill, where even shoes are optional. There are also a wide a wide selection of bars including two where you can remain in the pool and enjoy your cocktails, and a magical Emerald Tree Lounge that literally lights up each night. T<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe three buildings feature garden, mountain and ocean view rooms with available suites and concierge and butler service.<br />\r\nSince our resort in Jamaica is all-inclusive, your stay is hassle free. Jewel offers free transportation from Montego Bay, Jamaica - Sangster International Airport.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>What is included?</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Accommodation luxury rooms and suites with butler service<br />\r\n&bull; All meals and snacks at 6 restaurants from Jerk Chicken Gourmet Dining<br />\r\n&bull; Unlimited number of high quality beverages at 6 bars<br />\r\n&bull; Daily activities and entertainment<br />\r\n&bull; 9-hole pitch &amp; putt golf course in situ<br />\r\n&bull; free green fees at the championship (18) Hole Golf Club Runaway Bay<br />\r\n&bull; Free WiFi throughout the hotel<br />\r\n&bull; Non-motorized water sports<br />\r\n&bull; Weekly immersed in Movies<br />\r\n&bull; Volleyball and basketball<br />\r\n&bull; Fitness Room<br />\r\n&bull; 2 swimming pools with Epic Swim-up bar and outdoor concierge service<br />\r\nAirport transfers from Sangster International Airport in Montego Bay', '<strong>Dinner at Jewel </strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe formal Platinum to the most casual Aquamarina Beach Bar &amp; Grill, where even shoes are optional platinum, there are more than enough restaurants for every taste in the Jewel Dunn&#39;s River customize. It offers a world of culinary adventures six restaurants and six bars, our all-inclusive resort in Jamaica. Looking for an intimate dinner? Room Service, Free in suites or splurge on a dinner package at the private beach.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Casual Dining </strong><br />\r\n&bull; Aqua<br />\r\n&bull; Coral Caf&eacute;<br />\r\n&bull; Buffoon<br />\r\nDining room<br />\r\n&bull; Platinum<br />\r\n&bull; The Jade Samurai<br />\r\n&bull; Moonstone<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Bars and Lounges </strong><br />\r\n&bull; Aqua Marina<br />\r\n&bull; Emerald Tree Lounge<br />\r\n&bull; Sunken Treasure Swim-up bar<br />\r\n&bull; Boardwalk Bar<br />\r\n&bull; Jasper&#39;s Chillin Pool and Piano Bar<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>In Room Dining </strong><br />\r\n&bull; All day<br />\r\n&bull; Breakfast<br />\r\n&bull; Dinner<br />\r\nNight enjoyment', '', 'pool_horizontal_1938_00.jpg', '1405985615_', '1405985615_', NULL, NULL, 'Jewel-Resort-Dunns-River', 'Jewel Resort Dunns River Falls in an adults only resort located in Runaway bay Jamaica.', 'Jewel Dunns River, Jewel Resort Dunn''s Fiver Falls, Jewel Resort', '2014-07-21 16:33:36', 1, 13, 110, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0),
