(27, 'Deluxe Ocean Room', '<ul>\r\n	<li>King or Queen beds</li>\r\n	<li>Head boards with luxurious accents</li>\r\n	<li>Vanity armoire</li>\r\n	<li>Air conditioning (Individual climate control)</li>\r\n	<li>LCD screen TV</li>\r\n	<li>Satellite TV, with interactive menu, In-Room Movies</li>\r\n	<li>Telephone</li>\r\n	<li>Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Bathroom with shower and glass shower doors</li>\r\n	<li>Coffee maker</li>\r\n	<li>Hair dryer</li>\r\n	<li>Balcony or terrace</li>\r\n	<li>Iron and board</li>\r\n	<li>In-room bar stocked with: water, beer &amp; soft drinks</li>\r\n	<li>CD player/alarm clock</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 21, NULL, 'desire_deluxe1.jpg', 'deluxe-ocean-room', NULL, 0),
(28, 'Jacuzzi Suite Garden', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Welcome Fruit Basket and bottle of sparkling wine</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious bathroom with 4-person Jacuzzi</li>\r\n	<li>CD and DVD player (music and movies available at Front Desk)</li>\r\n	<li>Variety of sensual and exotic candles</li>\r\n	<li>Tantra essentials Gift Box</li>\r\n	<li>Desire incense</li>\r\n	<li>Daily afternoon hors d&acirc;&euro;&trade;oeuvres and sweet temptations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 21, NULL, 'desire_jacuzzi_suite0.jpg', 'jacuzzi-suite-garden', NULL, 0),
(29, 'Jacuzzi Suite Ocean ', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Welcome Fruit Basket and bottle of sparkling wine</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious bathroom with 4-person Jacuzzi</li>\r\n	<li>CD and DVD player (music and movies available at Front Desk)</li>\r\n	<li>Variety of sensual and exotic candles</li>\r\n	<li>Tantra essentials Gift Box</li>\r\n	<li>Desire incense</li>\r\n	<li>Daily afternoon hors d&acirc;&euro;&trade;oeuvres and sweet temptations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 21, NULL, 'desire_jacuzzi_suite1.jpg', 'jacuzzi-suite-ocean', NULL, 0),
(30, 'Ocean Front Passion Suite', '<p style="text-align:justify">Our 10 Passion Suites Oceanfront provide you with the most luxurious experience that goes beyond your imagination. Exquisitely decorated with sensual details inspired by the Kamasutra, including beautiful sculptures and paintings, will transport you to the promised land of unexpected pleasures. Enjoy unique moments of passion with your partner while relaxing in the Jacuzzi and be seduced by the most amazing views of the ocean and all the amenities these suites have been provided with. Including not only those who are in the Jacuzzi Suites, you will also discover a greater variety of special amenities in service of your desires, such as:&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Complimentary Private airport transfers</li>\r\n	<li>Concierge &quot;no-waiting&quot; check-in upon arrival</li>\r\n	<li>In-Room Daily Continental Breakfast</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited reservations for a table of 2-4 at the specialty restaurants</li>\r\n	<li>Adjacent living room</li>\r\n	<li>Daily afternoon hors d&#39;oeuvre with sparkling wine and fruit basket</li>\r\n	<li>Bathrobes and slippers</li>\r\n	<li>In-room Mini-bar stocked with: water, beer &amp; soft drinks, Tequila, Whisky, Vodka, Coffee Liquor and Bourbon.</li>\r\n	<li>Music and soft lighting upon arrival</li>\r\n	<li>Beach towels available in room</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 21, NULL, 'desire_passion_suite0.jpg', 'ocean-front-passion-suite', NULL, 0),
(31, 'Ocean View Room', '<p style="text-align:justify">Adding even more seduction to your clothing optional vacation with us, this beautiful and intimate room features a world of comforts such as a balcony or terrace and sitting area, bathroom with separate shower and bathtub as well as the following exclusive amenities.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A King sized bed or two Queen sized beds</li>\r\n	<li>300 thread-count Premium Cotton Bed Sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Private Balcony or Terrace</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious Living Area</li>\r\n	<li>International Cable TV and DVD/CD Player</li>\r\n	<li>In-room Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Cotton Bath Robes and Slippers</li>\r\n	<li>Two Telephones (in room and bathroom)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-conditioning with individual Climate Control</li>\r\n	<li>Alarm clock and radio</li>\r\n	<li>Ceiling Fan</li>\r\n	<li>Minibar Service</li>\r\n	<li>Hairdryer</li>\r\n	<li>Separate Shower and Bathtub</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 22, NULL, 'thum_ocean_front_rooms0.jpg', 'ocean-view-room-1', NULL, 0),
(32, 'Junior Suites', '<p style="text-align:justify">Surrounding you with a sensual and passion-evoking atmosphere, the Junior Suite will complement all the amenities of the hotel that are ideal for you to enjoy the most seductive clothing optional vacation in the Mexican Caribbean. This spacious and beautifully appointed suite features a sitting area, private balcony or terrace for relaxing or dining, shower and a separate bathtub that overlooks the room through shuttered doors, as well as the following, exclusive amenities.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A King sized bed or two Queen sized beds</li>\r\n	<li>300 thread-count Premium Cotton Bed Sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Private Balcony or Terrace</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious Living Area (Separate Living Area in Master Suites &amp; Penthouses)</li>\r\n	<li>International Cable TV and DVD/CD Player</li>\r\n	<li>In-room Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Cotton Bath Robes and Slippers</li>\r\n	<li>Two Telephones (in room and bathroom)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-conditioning with individual Climate Control</li>\r\n	<li>Alarm clock and radio</li>\r\n	<li>Ceiling Fan</li>\r\n	<li>Minibar Service</li>\r\n	<li>Hairdryer</li>\r\n	<li>Separate Shower and Bathtub</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 22, NULL, 'thum_rooms_junior_suite0.jpg', 'junior-suites', NULL, 0),
(33, 'Master Suite', '<p style="text-align:justify">This sensual suite boasts a large bedroom, a full bathroom with shower and a separate bathtub that overlooks the room through shuttered doors. Adding to the functionality and luxury of this suite, it has a cozy living room area with balcony or terrace, 42&quot; plasma TV, a work area and another full bathroom, plus the following exclusive amenities:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A King sized bed or two Queen sized beds</li>\r\n	<li>300 thread-count Premium Cotton Bed Sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Private Balcony or Terrace</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious Living Area (Separate Living Area in Master Suites &amp; Penthouses)</li>\r\n	<li>International Cable TV and DVD/CD Player</li>\r\n	<li>In-room Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Cotton Bath Robes and Slippers</li>\r\n	<li>Two Telephones (in room and bathroom)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-conditioning with individual Climate Control</li>\r\n	<li>Alarm clock and radio</li>\r\n	<li>Ceiling Fan</li>\r\n	<li>Minibar Service</li>\r\n	<li>Hairdryer</li>\r\n	<li>Separate Shower and Bathtub</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; color:rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; text-align:justify; vertical-align:middle; width:550px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 22, NULL, 'thum_rooms_master_suite0.jpg', 'master-suite', NULL, 0),
(34, 'Master Suite With Plunge Pool', '<p>These lavish suites, located on the ground floor, offer you and your couple a spacious bedroom, a cozy living room area with bar, 42&quot; plasma TV, a work area and a full bathroom. In addition, you will enjoy the serenity and dazzling views from the privacy of your own terrace, sun-lounge beds, plunge pool and a world of luxurious amenities including:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A King sized bed or two Queen sized beds</li>\r\n	<li>300 thread-count Premium Cotton Bed Sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Private Balcony or Terrace</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious Living Area (Separate Living Area in Master Suites &amp; Penthouses)</li>\r\n	<li>International Cable TV and DVD/CD Player</li>\r\n	<li>In-room Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Cotton Bath Robes and Slippers</li>\r\n	<li>Two Telephones (in room and bathroom)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-conditioning with individual Climate Control</li>\r\n	<li>Alarm clock and radio</li>\r\n	<li>Ceiling Fan</li>\r\n	<li>Minibar Service</li>\r\n	<li>Hairdryer</li>\r\n	<li>Separate Shower and Bathtub</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle"><img alt="Master Suites with Plunge Pool" src="http://desirepearl.originalresorts.com/img/desire-pearl-master_suite_pool.jpg" style="border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; height:450px; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 22, NULL, 'thum_rooms_master_suite_plunge0.jpg', 'master-suite-with-plunge-pool', NULL, 0),
(35, 'Penthouse Passion Suite', '<p>This exceptional one bedroom penthouse offers a wide variety of amenities that include inspiring ocean views and unparalleled luxury. With impeccable Mexican-Contemporary decor and an intimate ambiance, this exclusive suite is the perfect, intimate getaway for couples looking to rekindle the passion. Its separate living room area offers access to a private, wide panoramic terrace that feature its own plunge pool and a double chaise lounge to enjoy fantastic sunsets or romantic dinners under the stars. Relax in our Penthouses that have been designed to provide you and your couple with the most delicious spaces for those moments of intimacy. Other convenient amenities include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A King sized bed or two Queen sized beds</li>\r\n	<li>300 thread-count Premium Cotton Bed Sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Private Balcony or Terrace</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious Living Area (Separate Living Area in Master Suites &amp; Penthouses)</li>\r\n	<li>International Cable TV and DVD/CD Player</li>\r\n	<li>In-room Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Cotton Bath Robes and Slippers</li>\r\n	<li>Two Telephones (in room and bathroom)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-conditioning with individual Climate Control</li>\r\n	<li>Alarm clock and radio</li>\r\n	<li>Ceiling Fan</li>\r\n	<li>Minibar Service</li>\r\n	<li>Hairdryer</li>\r\n	<li>Separate Shower and Bathtub</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle"><img alt="Penthouse Passion Suites with Plunge Pool" src="http://desirepearl.originalresorts.com/img/desire-pearl-penthouse.jpg" style="border:0px; font-size:12px; font:inherit; height:450px; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; width:550px" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 22, NULL, 'thum_rooms_penthouse0.jpg', 'penthouse-passion-suite', NULL, 0),
(36, 'Seacliff Room', '<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:10px">&nbsp;All Seacliff rooms feature a large&nbsp;</span><a href="file://localhost/javascript/void(0)" style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-center; ">619 sq. ft. floor plan</a><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:10px">with two queen size or one king size bed, two upholstered chairs, end table, dresser, refrigerator tile bath with shower and patio or balcony.</span>', 23, NULL, 'sc_apt201_view4121.jpg', 'seacliff-room', NULL, 0),
(37, 'Seacliff Deluxe Room', '<h3>Seacliff Deluxe Studio</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Seacliff Deluxe Studios feature large&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-seacliff.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">748 sq. sf.</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-seacliff.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">759 sq. sf.</a>&nbsp;floor plans; each with two queen size or one king size bed, sitting area, dining area, Kitchen areas have a refrigerator, coffee makers, cabinets, sink and table setting. There are no cooking facility in any accommodation. All have tile bath with shower and patio or balcony.</p>\r\n', 23, NULL, 'studio-living-area1.jpg', 'seacliff-deluxe-room', NULL, 0),
(38, 'Seacliff One Bedroom', '<h3>These spacious two room suites offer a&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-seacliff.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">1183 sq. ft. floor plan</a>.&nbsp; Each have a living room with sofa, two chairs, coffee table, dining area. Kitchen areas have a refrigerator, coffee makers, cabinets, sink and table setting. There no cooking facility in any accommodation..&nbsp; Separate bedroom with two queen size or one king size bed, tile bath with shower and patio or balcony.</h3>\r\n', 23, NULL, 'accommodations_bath20.jpg', 'seacliff-one-bedroom', NULL, 0),
(39, 'One Bedroom Deluxe Villas', '<p>Private deluxe villas with&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-cove.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">812 sq. ft. floor plan</a>.&nbsp; One bedroom villas feature a living room with sofa, two chairs, coffee table, dining area. Kitchen areas have a refrigerator, coffee makers, cabinets, sink and table setting. There no cooking facility in any accommodation.&nbsp; All Villas have a separate bedroom with two queen size or one king size bed and tile bath with shower.</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 23, NULL, 'view-ocean-front-villa4120.jpg', 'one-bedroom-deluxe-villas', NULL, 0),
(40, 'Two Bedroom Villas', '<p>Private deluxe villas with&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-cove.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">1210 sq. sf.</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-cove.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">1304 sq. sf.</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="http://www.calienteresorts.com/caribe/accom-cove.html" style="color: rgb(22, 56, 124); text-decoration: none; ">1514 sq. sf.</a>&nbsp;floor plans. These limited two bedroom villas feature a living room with sofa, two chairs, coffee table, dining area and full kitchen.&nbsp; Kitchen areas have a refrigerator, coffee makers, cabinets, sink and table setting. There no cooking facility in any accommodation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All two bedroom Villas have a separate bedrooms with queen size beds and tile bath with shower.</p>\r\n', 23, NULL, 'ov_villa446_view4120.jpg', 'two-bedroom-villas', NULL, 0),
