(26, 'Dave', '<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">LadyDee, once again I would like to thank you for making my wife and I feel so welcome. With it being our first time booking with your group I can honestly say you and your staff are some of the nicest people I have ever had the pleasure to meet. Kim, Sara, your assistant, your Husband, and of course You, made this vacation fantastic. BTW thank you for booking Nina as well, she is so sweet and real. I&#39;m looking forward to next year already,</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Sincerely yours,</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Dave&nbsp;</span>', '', '2014-08-15', 1),
(25, 'Dee', '<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Hey Dee,</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">It&rsquo;s Debbie. Just wanted to tell you what an amazing time Bossy and I had and to thank you and Sarge for your kindness and hospitality. I was quite shy, but left there with a new attitude, outlook and confidence that&rsquo;s makes me feel incredible!</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Thank you so much for everything, we are looking forward to next year!! Hopefully it won&rsquo;t be that long before we see the two of you again&hellip;once again thank you and congratulations on a successful week</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">xoxo</span>', '', '2014-08-15', 1),
(24, 'Nicole and Dan', '<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">We were VERY impressed by the Kama Sutra group. It looked like so much fun and so much extra effort was put in to bring the group together. Therefore, we decided we definitely wanted to join you guys for 2013.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Anyway, please let us know what the next steps are.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Thanks so much<br />\r\nXOXO</span>', '', '2014-08-15', 1),
(20, 'Nina Hartley', '<p>Hedo Kamasutra week 2013 was my first-time ever trip to Jamaica and I had a blast! Sarge and Dee were wonderful and gracious hosts and couldn&#39;t have done more to make me feel at home. It was such fun to be back with my Swinger friends, as it&#39;s been a while since I got to hang out with a bunch of sexy folks who forgot their clothes! I loved teaching the workshops and people will be able to vote on which ones they want for next year. I can&#39;t wait to see how the new owners tweak what is an amazing, fun, sexy and friendly place. See you in 2014!&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: normal; font-family: ''times new roman'', ''new york'', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;">Nina</div>\r\n', 'deenina0.jpg', '2014-08-15', 1),
(21, 'John and Brenda', '<p><strong><em>&ldquo;This was our first trip with the Hedo Kamasutra group, but not our first to Hedo with a travel group . &nbsp;<br />\r\nLady Dee &amp; Sarge showed us &nbsp;there is &nbsp;difference between an okay &nbsp;group and an awesome one.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>From the time we arrived to the time we left LadyDee &amp; Sarge kept the party going, and instill in us how important their guest are to them.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>If you&rsquo;re up if the air about booking this Week don&rsquo;t be, unless your booking with some other group.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>This was the best Hedo trip we ever had! Thanks again &nbsp;LadyDee &amp; Sarge&hellip;is it next year yet?&rdquo;</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>John &amp; Brenda</em></strong></p>\r\n', '', '2014-08-15', 1),
(22, 'Dan and Joce', 'Just wanted to say thanks for the two weeks of vacation that you guys organize,we had a really good time, met good people that we&#39;ll probably be friends for a long time. Dan and Joce', '', '2014-08-15', 1),
(23, 'C & J ', '<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Hi, Dee &amp; Sarge</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Welcome Back! It was just an awesome trip!!!! We&#39;re having withdrawal too. You guys really did a fantastic job putting everything together.. Thank you so much for all you do. Also, thanks again for your help with the Mobay Lounge (it was ironic that all the names (Dee, Sarge, Hedo Kamasutra, Hedo) that we first used to verify our verification and we didn&#39;t use the most obvious one (Sunset Destinations) until they spoke with you.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">We&#39;ll definitely post a trip report on trip advisor and we&#39;re looking forward to 2013!</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Cheers,</span>', '', '2014-08-15', 1);
